%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'All%20India%20Rank'%3A%20Varun%20Grover%20Makes%20a%20Gentle%20Directorial%20Debut%20With%20a%20Film%20That%20is%20Not%20Quite%20Fulfilling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111118%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.10.07%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20found%20myself%20leaning%20into%20Varun%20Grover%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20India%20Rank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20an%20early%20scene.%20Vivek%20(Bodhisattva%20Sharma)%20has%20just%20reached%20the%20first%20day%20of%20his%20coaching%20class%20in%20Kota.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWoh%20ladkiyon%20ki%20seat%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(That%20seat%20is%20reserved%20for%20girls)%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20classmate%20tells%20him%20as%20he%E2%80%99s%20about%20to%20put%20his%20things%20down.%20He%20leaves%20two%20seats%20and%20sits%20adjacent%20to%20the%20stranger%20who%20prompted%20him.%20There%20are%20nerves%2C%20there%20is%20eagerness%2C%20there%20is%20promise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CExcited%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20classmate%20asks%20Vivek.%20He%20nods%20in%20acknowledgment.%20A%20nation%20is%20on%20the%20brink.%20The%20assembly%20line%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20CEOs%20has%20just%20about%20begun.%20Global%20domination%20is%20knocking%20on%20the%20door%2C%20and%20all%20one%20has%20to%20do%20is%20flash%20their%20IIT%20certificates%20at%20their%20gate%20and%20pass%20into%20the%20good%20life.%20It%20is%20what%20has%20been%20drilled%20into%20the%20kids%20of%20that%20generation.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20scene%20that%20becomes%20a%20time%20capsule%20of%20sorts%20%E2%80%93%20distilling%20the%20feeling%2C%20rather%20than%20logistically%20recreating%20the%20era.%20It%E2%80%99s%20this%20visceral%20feeling%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20India%20Rank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20first%20half%20could%E2%80%99ve%20used%20more%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FahttNxGnLsQ%3Fsi%3DljeqPDVrv_wz-Bbm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELyricist%2C%20writer%2C%20jester%20and%20now%20director%20Varun%20Grover%20reflects%20on%20the%20IIT%20rat%20race%20in%20his%20feature%20debut.%20A%20student%20of%20IIT-BHU%20(Banaras%20Hindu%20University)%20himself%2C%20Grover%20looks%20back%20on%20his%20journey%20with%20fondness%20and%20clarity%2C%20but%20also%20somewhere%20blurs%20the%20lines%20between%20objective%20truth%20and%20subjective%20experience.%20So%2C%20we%20get%20a%20film%20that%20feels%20forensic%20in%20its%20setting%2C%20but%20also%20feels%20nostalgic%20given%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20written%20with%20so%20much%20wisdom%20and%20kindness.%20It%E2%80%99s%20most%20apparent%20in%20the%20way%20Grover%20characterises%20Vivek%E2%80%99s%20parents%2C%20played%20by%20Shashi%20Bhushan%20and%20Geeta%20Agrawal.%20He%20remembers%20the%20casual%20cruelty%20inflicted%20on%20him%2C%20but%20he%20also%20tries%20to%20rationalise%20it%20by%20investigating%20where%20they%20were%20coming%20from.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMr%20Singh%20loves%20the%20smell%20of%20cigarettes%20but%20as%20a%20member%20of%20a%20painfully-inert%20middle%20class%2C%20he%20allows%20himself%20the%20indulgence%20to%20smoke%20only%20on%20public%20holidays%20(thrice%20every%20year).%20Mrs%20Singh%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20battles%20with%20her%20love%20for%20sweets%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20specifically).%20The%20father%20is%20a%20typical%20domineering%20figure%2C%20but%20Grover%20crafts%20multiple%20scenes%20to%20break%20this%20image.%20He%E2%80%99s%20shown%20to%20care%20for%20his%20wife%2C%20unexpectedly%20breaking%20into%20a%20laugh%20when%20she%20says%20something%20caustic%20about%20the%20humiliation%20he%E2%80%99s%20facing%20at%20the%20workplace.%20A%20mousy%20character%20in%20his%20office%20environs%20%E2%80%93%20someone%20who%20is%20unable%20to%20assert%20his%20identity%20fully%20%E2%80%93%20Mr%20Singh%20believes%20the%20news%20of%20his%20son%20making%20it%20to%20IIT%20will%20plug%20that%20hole%20in%20his%20heart%3A%20respect%20from%20his%20peers.%20But%20he%20soon%20rises%20above%20that%20delusion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111139%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.10.3-1024x420.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111139%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.10.3-1024x420.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111139%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.10.3-300x123.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111139%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.10.3.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22345%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98All%20India%20Rank%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20little%20doubt%20that%20Grover%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20gentle%20writers%20out%20there%2C%20but%20his%20directorial%20voice%20still%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20work-in-progress.%20Especially%20in%20the%20Kota%20portions%2C%20where%20the%20scenes%20seem%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20string%20of%20anecdotes%20without%20a%20connective%20tissue.%20The%20way%20the%20animation%20is%20used%20to%20communicate%20the%20inner-rumblings%20of%20the%20clueless%20teenager%2C%20reminded%20me%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EUdaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20still%20posters%20(minus%20the%20deftness).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBodhisattva%20Sharma%20as%20Vivek%20is%20earnest%20through%20most%20of%20his%20scenes%2C%20but%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20invest%20in%20him%20and%20his%20friends.%20They%20were%20versions%20of%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20earlier%20%E2%80%93%20the%20sneaky%20friend%20(Neeraj)%20secretly%20preparing%20for%20exams%20while%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20slacker%2C%20the%20female%20friend%20(Samta%20Sudhiksha)%20with%20that%20clarity%20to%20speak%20her%20mind%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98loser%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20group%20who%20has%20already%20checked%20out%20of%20the%20year.%20In%20the%20track%20unfolding%20in%20Kota%2C%20the%20film%20coasts%20along%20with%20studying%2Fslacking%20montages%2C%20never%20quite%20giving%20us%20a%20sense%20of%20time%20as%20it%20might%20be%20passing%20through%20a%20sand%20clock.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Grover%20showcases%20his%20observant%20side%20in%20more%20than%20one%20scene.%20Like%20when%20the%20teacher%20at%20the%20coaching%20class%2C%20played%20by%20Sheeba%20Chadha%2C%20plays%20%E2%80%98Papa%20Kehte%20Hai%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20coaching.%20In%20a%20room%20full%20of%20students%20carrying%20the%20burden%20of%20their%20families%E2%80%99%20expectations%2C%20the%20song%20gets%20a%20whole%20new%20perverse%20meaning.%20A%20creepy%20teenager%2C%20who%20likes%20making%20lewd%20phone%20calls%20to%20women%20in%20the%20area%20through%20a%20PCO%2C%20identifies%20himself%20as%20%E2%80%98Shawn%20Michaels%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20wrestling%20star.%20Late%20in%20the%20film%2C%20Vivek%20confesses%20everything%20his%20father%20says%20to%20him%20over%20the%20phone%20feels%20like%20a%20reminder%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98duty%E2%80%99%20of%20getting%20into%20IIT.%20All%20he%20hears%20over%20the%20phone%20is%20%E2%80%9CIIT%E2%80%A6%20IIT%E2%80%A6%20IIT.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111130%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.09.59%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x469.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111130%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.09.59%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x469.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111130%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.09.59%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x138.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27111130%2FScreenshot-2024-02-27-at-11.09.59%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699056%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22385%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98All%20India%20Rank%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrover%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20strongest%2C%20when%20it%20plays%20between%20Bhushan%20and%20Agrawal.%20Being%20suspended%20from%20his%20workplace%20for%20a%20botched%20errand%20%E2%80%93%20the%20cake%20for%20the%2050th%20Independence%20Day%20celebration%20has%20an%20inverted%20flag%20%E2%80%93%20Mr%20Singh%20has%20an%20awakening%20about%20how%20he%E2%80%99s%20funnelling%20his%20frustration%20onto%20his%20son.%20It%20results%20in%20a%20remarkably%20moving%20scene%20when%20he%2C%20using%20his%20awkward%20vocabulary%2C%20apologises%20to%20his%20son%20and%20cajoles%20him%20into%20not%20giving%20undue%20importance%20to%20the%20IIT%20entrance.%20Bhushan%20is%20terrific%20in%20the%20scene.%20And%20so%20is%20Agrawal%E2%80%93%20who%20finds%20a%20voice%20for%20the%20under%20confident%20Indian%20mothers%2C%20probably%20not%20articulate%20enough%20to%20v