visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108031100%2Cimgsize-152508.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Flee-jae-wook-and-aespas-karina-confirm-relationship%2Farticleshow%2F108031121.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108031121.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELee%20Jae%20Wook%20and%20aespa%E2%80%99s%20Karina%20sparked%20dating%20rumors%20after%20being%20seen%20together%20at%20the%20Prada%20fashion%20show%20in%20Milan.%20They%20reportedly%20had%20secret%20rendezvous%20in%20Lee%20Jae%20Wook%E2%80%99s%20neighborhood%20and%20were%20spotted%20on%20late-night%20strolls.%20CJes%20Studios%20and%20SM%20Entertainment%20have%20now%20confirmed%20the%20relationship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Flee-jae-wook-and-aespas-karina-confirm-relationship%2Farticleshow%2F108031121.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Solidarity%20Matters%3A%20What%20Connects%20Two%20Struggles%20in%20Asia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20writing%20this%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20I%20attended%20an%20interesting%20solidarity%20meeting.%20It%20was%20interesting%20because%20it%20combined%20two%20struggles%20%E2%80%94%20that%20for%20secularism%20in%20democratic%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0and%20against%20imperialism%20in%20occupied%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHosted%20by%20the%20Boston%20South%20Asian%20Coalition%20it%20featured%20two%20speakers.%20One%20was%20our%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20heroine%20of%20the%20struggle%20for%20justice%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20other%20was%20a%20young%20man%20from%20South%20Lebanon%20named%20Saleem%20Hallal.%20In%20the%20audience%20were%20a%20few%20dozen%20people%20including%20several%20desis%20and%20to%20my%20mind%20this%20was%20what%20made%20this%20gathering%20especially%20interesting%20and%20I%20will%20write%20about%20why%20that%20is%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20by%20the%20two%20speakers%20were%20focussed%20on%20the%20facts.%20About%20communal%20crimes%20in%20one%20place%20condoned%20by%20the%20state%20(some%20would%20say%20encouraged%20by%20it)%20and%20in%20the%20other%20a%20national%20struggle%20for%20liberation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20common%20thread%20and%20that%20was%20historical%20revisionism%20and%20the%20rewriting%20of%20things.%20The%20idea%20in%20both%20Palestine%20and%20%E2%80%98New%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99%20that%20something%20else%20used%20to%20be%20here%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20in%20this%20land%20a%20thousand%20years%20ago%20or%20two%20thousand%20years%20ago.%20And%20that%20idea%20and%20that%20notion%20therefore%20justifies%20violence%20against%20people%20and%20against%20structures%20and%20monuments%20in%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20the%20audience%20including%20myself%20found%20themselves%20nodding%20at%20the%20parallels.%20Setalvad%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20friend%20for%20a%20few%20decades%2C%20was%20precise%20and%20deliberate%20in%20what%20she%20communicated%20to%20the%20gathering%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20may%20not%20have%20known%20of%20what%20had%20transpired%20in%20and%20after%202002%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fteesta-setalvad-personal-plea-house-arrest-political-prisoners%5C%22%3EA%20Home%20Behind%20Bars%3A%20Teesta%20Setalvad%E2%80%99s%20Personal%20Plea%20for%20%E2%80%98House%20Arrest%E2%80%99%20for%20Political%20Prisoners%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20spoke%20of%20the%20174%20individuals%20who%20had%20been%20convicted%20because%20of%20the%20courage%20and%20persistence%20of%20the%20survivors%20and%20activists.%20Of%20these%20124%20were%20given%20life.%20These%20were%20convictions%20that%20came%20often%20in%20the%20face%20of%20resistance%20from%20the%20state%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20justice.%20To%20understand%20what%20sort%20of%20effort%20that%20took%2C%20consider%20only%20how%20rapist-murderer%20convicts%20are%20today%20mollycoddled%20by%20the%20government%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0which%20wants%20to%20release%20them%20for%20no%20reason%20other%20than%20bigotry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20might%20not%20know%20now%20and%20many%20who%20knew%20will%20have%20forgotten%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20moved%20trials%20out%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20something%20that%20to%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%20has%20not%20happened%20since%20or%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHallal%20spoke%20directly%20and%20with%20passion%20about%20how%20unjust%20was%20both%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Palestine%20and%20the%20falsity%20of%20the%20narrative%20constructed%20to%20sustain%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20early%20settlers%20into%20Israel%20survived%20because%20of%20the%20aid%20of%20Palestinians%20he%20said%2C%20just%20as%20the%20early%20settlers%20into%20America%20had.%20What%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20Territories%20was%20not%20a%20religious%20conflict%20but%20one%20of%20the%20occupied%20against%20the%20occupier.%20He%20exposed%20how%20hollow%20it%20was%20to%20describe%20the%20settler%20colonialism%20as%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98land%20without%20people%20for%20a%20people%20without%20a%20land%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20how%20the%20narrative%20that%20the%20Israel%20Palestine%20issue%20was%20%E2%80%98complicated%E2%80%99%20was%20merely%20something%20used%20to%20obscure%20a%20simple%20reality.%20That%20of%20occupation%20and%20colonialism%20and%20the%20rewriting%20of%20history%20with%20a%20particular%20agenda.%20The%20talk%20is%20on%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6f713251-1173-4ae6-a6c4-d7b16b7496d3%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6f713251-1173-4ae6-a6c4-d7b16b7496d3%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709087537871000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2R_T6EprUSE0pHUVRot6nV%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20South%20Asian%20Coalition%20YouTube%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20I%20would%20encourage%20all%20to%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3z-y2o5ttn4%3Fsi%3DTG3bvUfcmo2xHVvj%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20I%20said%20I%20found%20this%20gathering%20interesting%20was%20that%20it%20is%20not%20uncommon%20for%20Indian%20groups%20in%20the%20US%20to%20be%20shown%20as%20backing%20the%20government%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Particularly%20on%20such%20issues%20as%20what%20the%20government%20does%20to%20minority%20Indians%20and%20in%20events%20that%20are%20organised%20by%20the%20state%20(%E2%80%98Howdy%E2%80%99).%20This%20is%20especially%20and%20unfortunately%20true%20of%20my%20own%20Gujarati%20community%2C%20who%20are%20often%20shown%20as%20being%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20defence%20of%20state%20communalism.%20But%20there%20is%20another%20side%20to%20this%20and%20there%20are%20other%20Indians%2C%20many%20of%20them%2C%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20path%20we%20have%20taken%20in%20recent%20years.%20It%20is%20those%20who%20I%20joined%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20gathering%20I%20spoke%20briefly%20on%20what%20it%20was%20that%20Indians%20abroad%20could%20do.%20This%20was%20that%20they%20should%20use%20the%20democratic%20process%20in%20their%20country%20to%20engage%20with%20what%20was%20happening%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20The%20main%20reason%20that%20a%20discriminatory%20citizenship%20law%20was%20passed%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0in%202019%20but%20not%20implemented%20yet%20was%20the%20protest%20against%20it.%20But%20another%20reason%20was%20the%20condemnatory%20position%20taken%20against%20it%20by%20the%20European%20Parliament.%20One%20wonders%20why%20it%20was%20that%20MPs%20in%20far%20off%20lands%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20what%20we%20might%20think%20of%20as%20being%20as%20our%20%E2%80%98internal%20affairs%E2%80%99%20but%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20this%20was%20likely%20because%20Indians%20abroad%20were%20concerned%20enough%20to%20raise%20the%20law%20with%20their%20local%20legislator.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%20and%20the%20International%20Covenant%20on%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20our%20friends%20cannot%20remind%20us%20of%20this%20fact.%20And%20this%20in%20turn%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20happen%20if%20desis%20abroad%20engage%20more%20robustly%20with%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolidarity%20is%20important%20not%20only%20because%20as%20humans%20we%20should%20understand%20the%20suffering%20of%20others%20but%20because%20such%20participation%20is%20our%20duty.%20The%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20preamble%20says%20that%20we%20Indians%20have%20resolved%20to%20secure%20for%20Indians%20%E2%80%98fraternity%2C%20assuring%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20individual%E2%80%99.%20Fraternity%20can%20come%20only%20when%20we%20stand%20up%20for%20each%20other.%20The%20desis%20of%20the%20Boston%20South%20Asian%20Coalition%20actually%20attempt%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20an%20author%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709010383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsolidarity-matters-what-connects-two-struggles-in-asia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fraternity%20can%20come%20only%20when%20we%20stand%20up%20for%20each%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsolidarity-matters-what-connects-two-struggles-in-asia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oil%20spills%20pile%20on%20pressure%20for%20Iraq's%20farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709010015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108031046%2Cimgsize-1129616.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Foil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers%2Farticleshow%2F108030892.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108030892.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIraq%20enjoys%20tremendous%20oil%20wealth%20but%20many%20hard-scrabble%20farmers%20in%20the%20north%20say%20crude%20spills%20have%20contaminated%20their%20lands%2C%20piling%20on%20pressure%20as%20they%20already%20battle%20drought.%20Oil%20spills%20in%20Iraq%20--%20a%20country%20ravaged%20by%20decades%20of%20conflict%2C%20corruption%20and%20decaying%20infrastructure%20--%20have%20contaminated%20farmland%20in%20the%20northern%20province%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20winter%20rains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Foil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers%2Farticleshow%2F108030892.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Foil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers%2Famp_articleshow%2F108030892.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Foil-spills-pile-on-pressure-for-iraqs-farmers%2Famp_articleshow%2F108030892.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhip%26quot%3BLash%20For%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20On%20Key%20Poll%20Day%2C%20Hours%20After%20Dinner%20Surprise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20setback%20to%20Samajwadi%20Party%20ahead%20of%20the%20voting%20for%2010%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20its%20chief%20whip%20in%20the%20Assembly%20resigned%20this%20morning.%20The%20resignation%20of%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Pandey%2C%20MLA%20from%20Unchahar%2C%20came%20hours%20after%20as%20many%20as%208%20MLAs%20skipped%20a%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%C2%A0%20-%20a%20cause%20for%20worry%20amid%20the%20cross-voting%20buzz%20in%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Upper%20House.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20hitting%20the%20SP's%20prospects%20in%20this%20key%20election%2C%20cross-voting%20will%20compound%20the%20party's%20worries%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election.%20The%20SP%20will%20be%20contesting%2063%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20a%20mutiny%20months%20before%20the%20polls%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20blow.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20party's%20MLAs.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20how%20they%20work.%20They%20instil%20fear%2C%20threaten%20people%2C%20use%20agencies%20or%20take%20up%20any%20old%20case%20and%20pressure%20them.%20All%20these%20will%20not%20work%20in%20this%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20however%2C%20he%20was%20less%20confident.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20all%20three%20candidates%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20win.%20BJP%20can%20use%20all%20the%20tactics%20to%20win%20elections.%20BJP%20will%20do%20everything%20possible%20for%20victory.%20Some%20of%20our%20leaders%20who%20want%20personal%20gains%20can%20go%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2056%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20became%20vacant%20this%20year.%20Forty-one%20candidates%20were%20elected%20unopposed.%20Of%20the%20remaining%2C%2010%20are%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20four%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20one%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%2010%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%2011%20candidates%20are%20in%20the%20race%20--%208%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%203%20from%20main%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20confident%20of%20the%20victory%20of%20all%20its%20candidates%2C%20especially%20after%20it%20recently%20secured%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Jayant%20Chaudhary-led%20Rastriya%20Lok%20Dal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20support%20of%20Nishad%20Party%2C%20Suhel%20Dev%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20and%20Jansatta%20Dal.%20I%20am%20confident%20all%208%20NDA%20candidates%20will%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20BJP%20president%20Bhupendra%20Singh%20Chaudhary%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20had%20claimed%20that%20a%20section%20of%20SP%20legislators%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20them.%20The%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%20had%20denied%20this%2C%20but%20the%20absence%20of%20eight%20MLAs%20at%20last%20night's%20dinner%20has%20left%20the%20main%20Opposition%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20SP%20legislator%20Zahid%20Baig%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20did%20not%20come.%20Maybe%20they%20are%20busy.%20But%20if%20they%20have%20taken%20money%20(to%20cross-vote)%2C%20people%20will%20not%20forgive%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20eight%20candidates%20are%20former%20Union%20Minister%20RPN%20Singh%2C%20former%20MP%20Chaudhary%20Tejveer%20Singh%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20BJP's%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20unit%20Amarpal%20Maurya%2C%20former%20state%20minister%20Sangeeta%20Balwant%20(Bind)%2C%20party%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20former%20MLA%20Sadhna%20Singh%2C%20former%20Agra%20mayor%20Naveen%20Jain%20and%20Sanjay%20Seth.%20The%20SP%20has%20fielded%20actor%20MP%20Jaya%20Bachchan%2C%20retired%20IAS%20officer%20Alok%20Ranjan%20and%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman.%20The%20BJP%20has%20adequate%20numbers%20to%20get%20seven%20candidates%20elected%2C%20but%20its%20move%20to%20field%20an%20eighth%20has%20forced%20a%20contest.%20And%20it%20may%20succeed%20if%20cross-voting%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Happening%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Himachal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20candidates%20are%20in%20the%20contest%20for%20four%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20ruling%20Congress%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20three%20seats%2C%20and%20the%20BJP-JDS%20combine%20has%20the%20numbers%20to%20win%20at%20least%20one.%20But%20the%20Opposition%20alliance's%20naming%20of%20a%20second%20candidate%20has%20made%20it%20an%20exciting%20contest.%20Taking%20no%20changes%2C%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20has%20shifted%20its%20MLAs%20to%20a%20private%20hotel.%20State%20party%20chief%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20has%20denied%20any%20possibility%20of%20cro