C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20Southern%20Challenge%20As%20BJP%20Grapples%20Without%20Allies%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20tour%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20tomorrow%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20he%20has%20his%20task%20cut%20out%20to%20try%20and%20revive%20the%20political%20fortunes%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20party%2C%20with%20a%20negligible%203%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%2C%20is%20grappling%20without%20any%20major%20ally%20after%20AIADMK%20snapped%20its%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Dravidian%20arch-rivals%2C%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20its%20former%20ally%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20are%20keeping%20the%20BJP%20at%20arm's%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20only%20GK%20Vasan%2C%20chief%20of%20Tamil%20Maanila%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Indications%20suggest%20that%20Puthiya%20Thamizhagam%20and%20a%20few%20other%20smaller%20allies%20are%20mulling%20to%20switch%20to%20the%20DMK%20camp.%20Ousted%20AIADMK%20leaders%20O%20Panneerselvam%20(OPS)%2C%20Sasikala%2C%20and%20TTV%20Dhinakaran%2C%20are%20willing%20to%20join%20the%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20political%20rally%20at%20Palladam%20in%20Tiruppur%20district%20this%20afternoon%20would%20mark%20the%20culmination%20of%20BJP%20state%20unit's%20chief%20K%20Annamalai's%20padayatra%2C%20touching%20all%20233%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Braving%20odds%20and%20counting%20on%20PM%20Modi's%20influence%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20March%2C%20Mr%20Annamalai%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BForget%20who%20was%20with%20us%20then%20and%20now.%20When%20we%20started%20the%20rally%2C%20it%20was%20a%20BJP%20rally%3B%20now%20it%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20people's%20movement.%20More%20parties%20will%20join%20and%20strengthen%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20hands%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGK%20Vasan%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BOurs%20is%20a%20regional%20party%20with%20a%20national%20outlook%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20strengthen%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20hands%20to%20make%20India%20the%20third%20world%20economy%20and%20for%20the%20country's%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20failed%20in%20the%20Dravidian%20heartland%20in%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20is%20taking%20on%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20on%20issues%20of%20corruption%20and%20dynastic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20now%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20had%20swept%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20winning%2038%20of%20the%2039%20seats%2C%20and%20has%20kept%20its%20alliance%20intact.%20It%20is%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%2C%20raising%20issues%20of%20usurping%20rights%20of%20states%2C%20denying%20special%20relief%20packages%20to%20floods-ravaged%20Chennai%20and%20Tuticorin%2C%20%C2%A0price%20rise%2C%20and%20financial%20discrimination%20towards%20southern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%2C%20which%20had%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20last%20time%20and%20had%20lost%20both%20elections%20it%20fought%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20is%20fighting%20for%20the%20first%20time%20under%20the%20singular%20leadership%20of%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswamy%20(EPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20these%20challenges%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20addresses%20would%20be%20keenly%20watched%20to%20see%20if%20he%20would%20go%20beyond%20his%20pro-Tamil%20rhetoric%20to%20offer%20the%20state%20substantial%20financial%20and%20relief%20packages%20besides%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20long-standing%20demand%20for%20NEET%20exemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709009040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbsgmdn48_pm-modi-pti_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-southern-challenge-as-bjp-grapples-without-allies-in-tamil-nadu-5135071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20tour