%20balancing%20motherhood%20and%20her%20work%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20primary%20function%20is%20being%20a%20single%20mama%2C%26quot%3B%20Waddingham%20told%20People.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20keep%20saying%20to%20her%20that%20we%20are%20a%20team%20and%20that%20I%20have%20to%20do%20this.%20I%20have%20to%20strike%20while%20the%20iron%20is%20hot.%20I'm%20not%20so%20conceited%20that%20I%20would%20think%20that%20I%20will%20always%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20focus.%20I've%20always%20said%20to%20her%2C%20'Mommy%20must%20take%20this%20time%20while%20the%20light%20shines%20on%20me%2C%20because%20the%20light%20shines%20on%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaddingham%20also%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glamourmagazine.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fhannah-waddingham-glamour-women-of-the-year-awards-2023-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlamour%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202023%20that%20her%20relationship%20with%20her%20daughter's%20father%20ended%20when%20her%20daughter%20was%20around%20two-and-a-half%20years%20old%2C%20and%20that%20being%20a%20single%20mother%20in%20her%20forties%20wasn't%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20lie%2C%20it's%20quite%20exhausting.%20One%20of%20the%20greatest%20acting%20jobs%20in%20my%20life%20is%20pretending%20I%20have%20energy%20to%20my%20daughter!%26quot%3B%20Waddingham%20told%20Glamour.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20single%2C%20working%20mum%2C%20I%20won't%20deny%2C%20is%20hard.%20But%20I%20try%20to%20show%20my%20daughter%20every%20day%20that%20she%20is%20worth%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20my%20greatest%20achievement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Waddingham%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhannah-waddingham-sag-awards-daughter-handmade-cardboard-clutch-ted-lasso-2024-2%5C%22