.%E2%80%9D%20With%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20society%E2%80%99s%20increased%20reliance%20on%20social%20media%20to%20understand%20current%20world%20events%2C%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20has%20never%20been%20greater.%20In%20particular%2C%20in%20alignment%20with%20the%20recent%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%E2%80%99s%20preliminary%20ruling%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20brought%20against%20Israel%2C%20we%20implore%20Meta%20to%20take%20drastic%20measures%20to%20ensure%20your%20platforms%20are%20not%20contributing%20to%20harm%20and%20violence%20for%20anyone%20in%20Palestine%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20we%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20revision%20of%20its%20hate%20speech%20policy%20regarding%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CZionist%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20potential%20to%20treat%20it%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20Jewish%20and%2For%20Israeli%2C%20which%20will%20ultimately%20lead%20to%20severe%20restrictions%20on%20legitimate%20political%20speech%20and%20debate.%20%E2%80%9CZionist%E2%80%9D%20cannot%20be%20separated%20from%20the%20political%20ideology%20of%20%E2%80%9CZionism%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20both%20terms%20are%20explicitly%20unique%20and%20different%20from%20Jewish%20and%2For%20Israeli%20identities.%20The%20proposed%20policy%20would%20too%20easily%20mischaracterize%20conversations%20about%20Zionists%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%20extension%2C%20Zionism%20%E2%80%94%20as%20inherently%20antisemitic%2C%20harming%20Meta%20users%20and%20undermining%20efforts%20to%20dismantle%20real%20antisemitism%20and%20all%20forms%20of%20racism%2C%20extremism%20and%20oppression.%20Treating%20%E2%80%9CZionist%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20proxy%20will%20also%20encourage%20the%20incorrect%20and%20harmful%20conflation%20of%20criticism%20of%20the%20acts%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20with%20antisemitism.%20We%20cannot%20dismantle%20antisemitism%20if%20we%20are%20blocked%20from%20voicing%20our%20opinions%20and%20sharing%20our%20experiences%20with%20each%20other.%20We%20can%20discuss%2C%20debate%20and%20even%20disagree%2C%20as%20long%20as%20we%20share%20the%20belief%20that%20all%20of%20us%20deserve%20safety%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20dignity.%20We%20ask%20Meta%20to%20not%20erect%20barriers%20impeding%20users%20from%20connecting%20with%20each%20other%20as%20we%20engage%20in%20this%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20wrong%20solution%20to%20a%20real%20and%20important%20problem%3A%20those%20who%20fuel%20antisemitism%20online%20will%20continue%20doing%20so%2C%20with%20or%20without%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9CZionist.%E2%80%9D%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20antisemites%2C%20especially%20among%20white%20supremacists%20and%20evangelical%20Christian%20Zionists%2C%20explicitly%20support%20Zionism%20and%20Israel%2C%20while%20engaging%20in%20speech%20and%20actions%20that%20dehumanize%2C%20insult%2C%20and%20isolate%20Jewish%20people.%20Importantly%2C%20this%20move%20will%20prohibit%20Palestinians%20from%20sharing%20their%20daily%20experiences%20and%20histories%20with%20the%20world%2C%20be%20it%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20keys%20to%20their%20grandparent%E2%80%99s%20house%20lost%20when%20attacked%20by%20Zionist%20militias%20in%201948%2C%20or%20documentation%20and%20evidence%20of%20genocidal%20acts%20in%20Gaza%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20authorized%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Cabinet%2C%20which%20includes%20members%20of%20the%20Religious%20Zionist%20Party.%20And%20it%20would%20prevent%20Jewish%20users%20from%20discussing%20their%20relationships%20to%20Zionist%20political%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20proposed%20policy%20change%20won%E2%80%99t%20keep%20any%20of%20us%20safe%2C%20and%20does%20not%20align%20with%20normative%20international%20human%20rights%20standards.%20Furthermore%2C%20since%20the%20War%20on%20Gaza%20began%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20incitement%20to%20violence%20online%20against%20Palestinians%20is%20at%20an%20all%20time%20high.%20Not%20only%20will%20this%20proposal%20be%20ineffective%20at%20combating%20antisemitism%2C%20it%20entirely%20ignores%20the%20digitally%20fueled%20oppression%20of%20Palestinians%20at%20a%20time%20when%20multiple%20courts%20and%20human%20rights%20experts%20around%20the%20world%20have%20affirmed%20the%20plausibility%20that%20a%20genocide%20is%20happening%20in%20Gaza%20and%20ordered%20all%20international%20actors%20to%20do%20whatever%20they%20can%20to%20prevent%20further%20harm.%20We%20call%20upon%20Meta%20to%20recognize%20its%20crucial%20role%20and%20responsibility%2C%20to%20adhere%20to%20business%20and%20human%20rights%20principles%20as%20well%20as%20international%20human%20rights%20laws%20in%20safeguarding%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20and%20to%20not%20treat%20%E2%80%9CZionist%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20proxy%20in%20your%20hate%20speech%20policy%20but%20instead%20implement%20policy%20changes%20that%20will%20actually%20create%20a%20safer%20digital%20space%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7amleh%20%E2%80%93%20Arab%20Center%20for%20the%20Advancement%20of%20Social%20Media%3Cbr%3E%5Cn18%20Million%20Rising%20(18MR)%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccess%20Now%3Cbr%3E%5CnAction%20Center%20on%20Race%20and%20the%20Economy%2C%20(ACRE)%3Cbr%3E%5CnAdalah%20Justice%20Project%3Cbr%3E%5CnAl-Haq%3Cbr%3E%5CnAlhudood%3Cbr%3E%5CnAlternatives%20(Canada)%3Cbr%3E%5CnALTSEAN-Burma%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmerican-Arab%20Anti-Discrimination%20Committee%20(ADC)%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmerican%20Friends%20Service%20Committee%20(AFSC)%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmerican%20Muslims%20for%20Palestine%20(AMP)%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmnesty%20International%3Cbr%3E%5CnAssociation%20for%20Progressive%20Communications%20(APC)%3Cbr%3E%5CnBolo%20Bhi%3Cbr%3E%5CnBoycott%20from%20Within%3A%20Israeli%20Citizens%20for%20BDS%3Cbr%3E%5CnCenter%20for%20Constitutional%20Rights%3Cbr%3E%5CnCommittee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20(CPJ)%3Cbr%3E%5CnCommunity%20Media%20Network%3Cbr%3E%5CnCommunity%20Movement%20Builders%3Cbr%3E%5CnCouncil%20on%20American-Islamic%20Relations%20(CAIR)%3Cbr%3E%5CnDARAJ%20MEDIA%3Cbr%3E%5CnDigit