came%20to%20an%20unexpected%20halt%2C%20only%20to%20be%20ambushed%20by%20a%20mysterious%20i20%20car.%20A%20cinematic%20scene%20ensued%20as%20five%20men%20emerged%2C%20unleashing%20a%20hail%20of%20bullets%20upon%20the%20SUV.%20The%2066-year-old%20Mr%20Rathi%20and%20a%20loyal%20aide%20were%20killed%2C%20while%20two%20others%20fought%20for%20survival%20in%20critical%20condition.%20The%20assailants%20spared%20the%20life%20of%20Mr%20Rathi's%20nephew%2C%20who%20was%20driving%20the%20vehicle%2C%20instructing%20him%20to%20inform%20the%20family%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20now%20on%20a%20manhunt%20for%20the%20elusive%20i20%20which%20swiftly%20fled%20the%20scene%20following%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20new%20individuals%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%20are%20Virendra%20Rathi%2C%20Sandeep%20Rathi%2C%20and%20Rajpal%20Sharma%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20to%2015%20suspects%20-%2010%20known%2C%20including%20former%20BJP%20MLA%20Naresh%20Kaushik%2C%20and%20five%20unknown.%20According%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20two%20out%20of%20the%20three%20newly%20named%20individuals%20have%20political%20affiliations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20taken%20an%20international%20turn%20with%20suspicions%20pointing%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20notorious%20gangster%20based%20in%20the%20UK.%20This%20gangster%20has%20allegedly%20orchestrated%20political%20murders%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20that%20of%20a%20BJP%20leader%20in%20Delhi%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20Haryana%20Police%20will%20question%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20the%20UK-based%20gangster%20today%20currently%20incarcerated%20in%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%20Police's%20Probe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20suspects%20the%20potential%20involvement%20of%20sharpshooters%20associated%20with%20jailed%20gangsters%2C%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20Kala%20Jathedi%2C%20in%20the%20brutal%20killing%20of%20the%20INLD%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police's%20Crime%20Branch%20and%20Special%20Cell%2C%20working%20collaboratively%20on%20interstate%20gangsters'%20networks%2C%20have%20visited%20the%20crime%20scene%20in%20Jhajjar.%20At%20least%20five%20teams%20from%20the%20Special%20Cell%20and%20four%20from%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20have%20been%20actively%20coordinating%20with%20their%20counterparts%20in%20Haryana%20to%20probe%20the%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20other%20foreign-based%20gangsters%2C%20such%20as%20Himanshu%20Bhau%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20residing%20in%20Portugal%2C%20is%20not%20being%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20suspected%20that%20gang%20members%20of%20jailed%20gangsters%20might%20have%20taken%20the%20contract%20to%20eliminate%20Rathi%20for%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20Delhi%20police%20official%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gangs%20associated%20with%20Bishnoi%20and%20Jathedi%20are%20known%20for%20engaging%20in%20extortion%20and%20contract%20killings%20across%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20execution-style%20employed%20in%20Mr%20Rathi's%20murder%20resembles%20previous%20incidents%2C%20particularly%20the%20killing%20of%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20chief%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%2C%20suggesting%20a%20common%20modus%20operandi.%20The%20shooters%20associated%20with%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi-Godly%20Brar%20gang%20reportedly%20used%20foreign-made%20Zigana%20and%20Beretta%20pistols%20in%20both%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBI%20To%20Step%20In%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij%20on%20Monday%20announced%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20that%20the%20investigation%20would%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20House%20is%20only%20satisfied%20with%20a%20CBI%20probe%2C%20then%20I%20assure%20the%20members%20that%20we%20will%20hand%20over%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vij%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20fallout%20from%20the%20incident%20has%20been%20swift%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20demanding%20a%20high%20court%20judge-monitored%20CBI%20probe%20into%20Mr%20Rathi's%20murder.%20The%20incident%2C%20termed%20by%20the%20opposition%20as%20the%20state's%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20political%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20ignited%20a%20fierce%20debate%20on%20the%20adequacy%20of%20security%20measures%20provided%20to%20Mr%20Rathi%2C%20who%20had%20reportedly%20sought%20protection%20due%20to%20threats%20on%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20led%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20in%20paying%20tributes%20to%20the%20INLD%20chief%20on%20Monday%2C%20vowing%20to%20bring%20the%20culprits%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709001600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F9spvhtdg_inld-leader_625x300_26_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-murder-uk-based-gangster-could-be-behind-inld-chiefs-chilling-murder-police-5134559%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20gangster%20based%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20is%20likely%20behind%20the%20sensational%20murder%20of%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20chief%20Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20three%20more%20individuals%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-murder-uk-based-gangster-could-be-behind-inld-chiefs-chilling-murder-police-5134559%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-murder-uk-based-gangster-could-be-behind-inld-chiefs-chilling-murder-police-5134559%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-murder-uk-based-gangster-could-be-behind-inld-chiefs-chilling-murder-police-5134559%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Religious%20freedom%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20taken%20away%20by%20arbitrary%20action%20of%20state%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709001536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108027959%2Cimgsize-94740.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fallahabad%2Fhc-dismisses-aims-plea-allows-puja-inside-gyanvapi-basement%2Farticleshow%2F108026452.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20appeal%20by%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%20challenging%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20judge's%20order%20allowing%20puja%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20Vyas%20Tehkhana.%20The%20court%20found%20the%201993%20order%20stopping%20puja%20to%20be%20illegal%20and%20a%20continuous%20wrong%20perpetuated%20by%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAJESH%20KUMAR%20PANDEY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fallahabad%2Fhc-dismisses-aims-plea-allows-puja-inside-gyanvapi-basement%2Farticleshow%2F108026452.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Diplomats%20Were%20%26quot%3BThreatened%2C%20Intimidated%26quot%3B%20In%20Canada%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20expects%20action%20against%20the%20culprits%20involved%20in%20last%20year's%20attacks%20on%20its%20high%20commission%20in%20London%20and%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20as%20well%20as%20those%20involved%20in%20threatening%20the%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Monday%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20India%20had%20to%20suspend%20issuance%20of%20visas%20in%20Canada%20as%20its%20diplomats%20were%20repeatedly%20%26quot%3Bthreatened%20and%20intimidated%20in%20many%20ways%26quot%3B%20and%20we%20%26quot%3Bgot%20very%20little%20comfort%20from%20the%20Canadian%20system%20that%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20last%20year%2C%20India%20temporarily%20suspended%20issuance%20of%20visas%20to%20the%20Canadian%20citizens%2C%20a%20move%20that%20came%20days%20after%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20separatist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visa%20services%20were%20resumed%20several%20weeks%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20strongly%20rejected%20Trudeau's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20asserting%20its%20%26quot%3Bcore%20issue%26quot%3B%20with%20Canada%20remained%20that%20of%20the%20space%20given%20to%20the%20separatists%2C%20terrorists%20and%20anti-India%20elements%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20culprits%20in%20the%20attack%20in%20our%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20to%20be%20brought%20to%20book%2C%20we%20expect%20action%20against%20people%20who%20stormed%20into%20our%20high%20commission%20in%20London%20and%20we%20expect%20action%20against%20people%20who%20threatened%20our%20diplomats%20(in%20Canada)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20at%20a%20summit%20organised%20by%20TV9%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20London%20was%20attacked%20by%20certain%20pro-Khalistani%20elements%20in%20March%2019%20last%20year%20while%20there%20was%20an%20attempted%20arson%20at%20the%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20diplomats%20faced%20threats%20in%20Canada%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20suspend%20issuance%20of%20visas%20in%20Canada%20because%20our%20diplomats%20were%20not%20safe%20going%20to%20work.%20Our%20diplomats%20were%20repeatedly%20threatened.%20They%20were%20intimidated%20in%20many%20ways%20and%20we%20got%20very%20little%20comfort%20from%20the%20Canadian%20system%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reached%20a%20stage%20when%20as%20a%20minister%2C%20I%20could%20not%20risk%20exposing%20the%20diplomats%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20violence%20which%20was%20very%20clearly%20prevalent%20in%20Canada%20at%20that%20time.%20That%20part%20of%20it%20has%20been%20rectified.%20Today%2C%20our%20visa%20operations%20are%20pretty%20much%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20situation%20has%20improved%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20space%20given%20to%20the%20Khalistani%20elements%20in%20Canada%2C%20he%20cited%20instances%20of%20throwing%20of%20smoke%20bombs%20into%20the%20Indian%20missions%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Canada)%20keep%20telling%20us%20that%20we%20are%20a%20democracy.%20There%20is%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20people%20say%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFreedom%20of%20speech%20cannot%20extend%20to%20intimidating%20diplomats%20who%20are%20doing%20their%20duty.%20Throwing%20smoke%20bombs%20to%20embassy%20and%20consulates%2C%20advocating%20violence%20and%20separatism%20against%20a%20friendly%20state%20is%20not%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20this%20is%20misuse%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20culprits%20involved%20in%20these%20attacks%20must%20be%20brought%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20UK%2C%20we%20actually%20saw%20our%20high%20commission%20being%20attacked%20by%20mobs%20and%20honestly%20we%20did%20not%20get%20the%20kind%20of%20protection%20which%20we%20expected%20to%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn