Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzee-saga-sony-s-spurned-target-shows-pitfalls-of-tempting-indian-m-a-124022700057_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzee-saga-sony-s-spurned-target-shows-pitfalls-of-tempting-indian-m-a-124022700057_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20Resigned%20As%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Chairman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPaytm%20CEO%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20on%20Monday%20resigned%20as%20non-executive%20chairman%20and%20board%20member%20of%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20amid%20ongoing%20regulatory%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20digital%20payments%20giant.%20The%20decision%20follows%20a%20series%20of%20measures%20imposed%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20including%20an%20order%20for%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20wind%20down%20operations%20by%20March%2015%20due%20to%20persistent%20compliance%20issues%20and%20supervisory%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI's%20action%20against%20the%20payments%20bank%20stemmed%20from%20various%20concerns%2C%20including%20inadequate%20customer%20identity%20checks%20and%20a%20perceived%20lack%20of%20arms-length%20distance%20from%20the%20parent%20company%2C%20Paytm.%20These%20issues%20prompted%20a%20major%20board%20overhaul%2C%20with%20former%20chairman%20of%20Central%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20Srinivasan%20Sridhar%2C%20former%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20Executive%20Director%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Garg%2C%20and%20two%20retired%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officers%20joining%20the%20payments%20bank's%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm's%20decision%20to%20reconstruct%20the%20board%20with%20independent%20and%20executive%20directors%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20demonstrate%20compliance%20with%20regulatory%20norms%20and%20salvage%20the%20situation.%20While%20the%20RBI%20did%20not%20explicitly%20mandate%20the%20board%20reconstruction%2C%20it%20is%20speculated%20that%20the%20move%20aims%20to%20reassure%20the%20regulatory%20body%20about%20Paytm's%20commitment%20to%20adhering%20to%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20Quit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20owns%20a%2051%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20while%20One%2097%20Communications%2C%20as%20Paytm%20was%20formally%20known%2C%20owns%20the%20rest.%20Mr%20Sharma%20said%20that%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20board%20and%20the%20appointment%20of%20independent%20directors%20were%20strategic%20steps%20to%20enable%20a%20smooth%20transition%20and%20enhance%20governance%20structures.%20The%20move%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20disassociate%20Paytm%20from%20its%20payments%20bank%20unit%20and%20position%20it%20as%20an%20independent%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulatory%20challenges%20faced%20by%20Paytm%20have%20impacted%20its%20stock%20value%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20drop%20since%20the%20RBI's%20order.%20However%2C%20the%20stock%20has%20shown%20signs%20of%20recovery%2C%20attributed%20to%20Paytm's%20partnership%20with%20new%20banking%20entities%20and%20the%20RBI%20extending%20the%20deadline%20for%20winding%20down%20the%20payment%20bank's%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman's%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20on%20Monday%20convened%20a%20meeting%20with%20representatives%20from%20the%20fintech%20industry%20to%20discuss%20their%20concerns%20and%20issues.%20However%2C%20the%20developments%20at%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20were%20not%20specifically%20addressed%20during%20this%20meeting%2C%20according%20to%20two%20government%20officials%20who%20were%20present%2C%20reports%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20finance%20ministry%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20hold%20discussions%20with%20Indian%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20fintech%20firms%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20This%20upcoming%20meeting%20aims%20to%20facilitate%20communication%20between%20fintech%20firms%20and%20various%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concerns%20raised%20by%20some%20listed%20fintech%20companies%20regarding%20their%20ownership%20structures%20will%20be%20examined%20by%20both%20the%20central%20bank%20and%20the%20government.%20This%20move%20signals%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20enhance%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20fintech%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20government%20has%20pledged%20to%20simplify%20'know%20your%20customer'%20(KYC)%20norms%20across%20the%20fintech%20space.%20Simplifying%20KYC%20requirements%20could%20streamline%20onboarding%20processes%20for%20users%2C%20potentially%20addressing%20some%20of%20the%20operational%20challenges%20faced%20by%20fintech%20firms.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708996800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fanf18b2g_vijay-shekhar-sharma-paytm-_625x300_27_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-why-paytm-ceo-vijay-shekhar-sharma-quit-payments-bank-board-5134319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paytm%20CEO%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20on%20Monday%20resigned%20as%20non-executive%20chairman%20and%20board%20member%20of%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20amid%20ongoing%20regulatory%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20digital%20payments%20giant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-why-paytm-ceo-vijay-shekhar-sharma-quit-payments-bank-board-5134319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-why-paytm-ceo-vijay-shekhar-sharma-quit-payments-bank-board-5134319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fexplained-why-paytm-c