37%20Max%209%20planes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-airlines-boeing-flight-blowout-nstb-recovers-cellphones-door-plug-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblew%20off%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20preliminary%20report%20recently%20determined%20%3Cspan%3Ebolts%20that%20would%20have%20held%20the%20door%20in%20place%20weren't%20attached%20before%20the%20plane%20took%20off%20on%20January%205%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-airlines-boeing-737-blowout-missing-bolts-ntsb-investigation-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebefore%20it%20was%20even%20delivered%20by%20Boeing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20March%202023%20to%20February%202024%2C%20the%20FAA's%20expert%20panel%20of%20investigators%20reviewed%20Boeing%20documents%2C%20visited%20its%20facilities%2C%20and%20interviewed%20employees%20at%20all%20levels%20to%20determine%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20company's%20safety%20culture.%20They%20focused%20specifically%20on%20the%20engineering%20employees%20whose%20job%20it%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20company%20is%20complying%20with%20FAA%20guidelines%20under%20an%20agreement%20that%20allows%20Boeing%20to%20self-certify%20its%20own%20aircraft%2C%20which%20the%20FAA%20granted%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20more%20damning%20findings%20outlined%20in%20the%20FAA's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMajor%20faults%20in%20Boeing's%20safety%20management%20systems%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FAA%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20bosses%20in%20charge%20of%20employees'%20salaries%20were%20also%20overseeing%20those%20staffers'%20safety%20concerns%2C%20creating%20a%20culture%20where%20the%20employees%20hesitated%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20fear%20of%20retaliation%2C%20the%20panel%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expert%20panel%20found%20that%20many%20of%20Boeing's%20employees%2C%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20the%20company%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20the%20company's%20safety%20culture%20efforts%20and%20procedures%2C%20nor%20did%20they%20grasp%20their%20purpose.%20Staff%20also%20did%20not%20know%20their%20role%20in%20the%20safety%20management%20systems%2C%20and%20were%20skeptical%20of%20the%20systems'%20lasting%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20said%20it%20could%20not%20pinpoint%20a%20consistent%20and%20clear%20process%20for%20employees%20to%20report%20safety%20concerns.%20Not%20only%20did%20employees%20not%20understand%20how%20and%20when%20to%20use%20the%20proper%20reporting%20channels%2C%20but%20they%20also%20chose%20not%20to%20use%20them%20altogether.%20Instead%2C%20they%20simply%20brought%20their%20concerns%20to%20their%20managers%2C%20which%20doesn't%20allow%20for%20a%20systematic%20way%20to%20address%20and%20fix%20the%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20found%20Boeing's%20documentation%20of%20its%20safety%20management%20systems%20overly%20complex%20and%20constantly%20changing%2C%20which%20created%20a%20culture%20of%20confusion%20among%20the%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20not%20been%20successful%20at%20retaining%20key%20staff%20members%20who%20oversee%20the%20self-certification%20process%2C%20and%20has%20not%20been%20filling%20open%20roles%20quickly%20enough%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20panel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20orders%20Boeing%20to%20come%20up%20with%20an%20action%20plan%20within%20the%20next%20six%20months%20to%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensively%20address%20each%20recommendation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20made%2053%20total%20recommendations%20for%20how%20the%20company%20should%20not%20just%20improve%20its%20lackluster%20safety%20practices%2C%20but%20bring%20them%20up%20to%20the%20legal%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Boeing%20said%20that%20it%20has%20implemented%20a%20number%20of%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20changes%26quot%3B%20since%202019%20%26quot%3Bto%20strengthen%20product%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20more%20work%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20carefully%20review%20the%20panel's%20assessment%20and%20learn%20from%20their%20findings%2C%20as%20we%20continue%20our%20comprehensive%20efforts%20to%20improve%20our%20safety%20and%20quality%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigated-boeings-safety-culture-and-the-results-arent-great-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708986519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd019f90413ab8e1d6f7a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigated-boeings-safety-culture-and-the-results-arent-great-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20panel%20of%20experts%20found%20a%20number%20of%20faults%20in%20Boeing%20safety%20management%20systems%2C%20including%20a%20culture%20of%20confusion%20among%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigated-boeings-safety-culture-and-the-results-arent-great-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20right%20side%20of%20law%2C%20no%20need%20for%20shrine%20stir%3A%20VHP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708986300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108023357%2Cimgsize-1213082.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fon-right-s