ll%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Asus%20ZenScreen%20MB16AHG%20is%20a%20great%20all-around%20portable%20display.%20It%20fits%20most%20use%20cases%2C%20and%20there's%20not%20much%20it%20doesn't%20do%20well%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20best-in-class%20for%20any%20particular%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20average%20size%20and%20weight%20for%20a%20portable%20monitor%20(just%20a%20hair%20over%20two%20pounds).%20And%20it%20serves%20up%20Full%20HD%20(1080p)%20resolution%20with%20decent%20brightness%20on%20an%20LED%20panel.%20Going%20with%20a%20thinner%20or%20lighter%20model%20%E2%80%94%20or%20upgrading%20to%20a%20higher%20resolution%20or%20better%20display%20type%20%E2%80%94%20will%20cost%20more%2C%20and%20we%20think%20the%20MB16AHG%20delivers%20a%20great%20balance%20between%20value%20and%20performance%20for%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20a%20speedy%20three-millisecond%20response%20time%20and%20a%20fast%20144Hz%20refresh%20rate%2C%20both%20above%20entry-level%20standards.%20Along%20with%20FreeSync%20technology%2C%20these%20specifications%20ensure%20that%20this%20ZenScreen%20can%20deliver%20a%20quick%20and%20smooth%20experience%20that's%20even%20suitable%20for%20gamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20the%20monitor%20comes%20with%20decent%20audio%20options%2C%20thanks%20to%20built-in%20speakers%20and%20an%20audio%20jack%20for%20listening%20on%20headphones.%20And%20for%20video%2C%20it%20can%20connect%20to%20devices%20via%20USB-C%20or%20Mini%20HDMI.%20The%20USB%20connection%20is%20also%20how%20the%20display%20receives%20power%2C%20either%20through%20a%20connected%20laptop%20or%20to%20a%20wall%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MB16AHG%20has%20also%20been%20built%20with%20ergonomics%20in%20mind.%20A%20handy%20fold-out%20stand%20allows%20for%20tilting%20at%20multiple%20angles%2C%20and%20a%20threaded%20socket%20in%20the%20back%20allows%20it%20to%20be%20mounted%20to%20any%20standard%20tripod.%20The%20screen%20automatically%20orients%20to%20portrait%20or%20landscape%2C%20which%20is%20a%20given%20for%20phones%20nowadays%20but%20not%20always%20for%20portable%20monitors.%20And%20it's%20T%C3%9CV%20Rheinland-certified%20(the%20industry%20standard)%20to%20reduce%20eye%20strain%20through%20flicker-free%20and%20low%20blue%20light%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it's%20not%20quite%20as%20affordable%20as%20our%20budget%20pick%20just%20below%2C%20the%20ZenScreen%20MB16AHG%20is%20the%20best%20portable%20monitor%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20a%20great%20all-around%20display%20that%20performs%20well%20for%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EViewSonic's%20VA1655%20undercuts%20every%20other%20portable%20monitor%20on%20this%20list.%20Though%20it%20doesn't%20do%20anything%20%3Cem%3Ebetter%3C%2Fem%3E%20than%20our%20other%20picks%2C%20it%20delivers%20impressive%20specs%20for%20its%20low%20price%2C%20making%20it%20a%20worthy%20alternative%20for%20shoppers%20who%20want%20to%20spend%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20strong%20point%20in%20its%20favor%20is%20that%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20lightest%20options%20we%20recommend%2C%20at%20just%201.5%20pounds.%20And%20like%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20VA1655%20features%20a%2015.6-inch%20screen%20with%201080p%20resolution.%20On%20the%20downside%2C%20its%20seven-millisecond%20response%20time%20is%20slightly%20slower%20than%20pricier%20models%2C%20but%20the%20average%20student%20or%20remote%20worker%20probably%20won't%20notice%20any%20screen%20lag.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20monitor's%20peak%20brightness%20is%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bunch%2C%20just%20on%20the%20OK%20side%20of%20what's%20acceptable%2C%20which%20means%20it's%20fine%20for%20use%20indoors%20but%20won't%20be%20a%20good%20match%20for%20bright%20sunlight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20got%20a%20lower%20native%20bit%20depth%20than%20our%20other%20picks%2C%20which%2