4408%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42525%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-portable-monitor%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Frog.asus.com%252Fus%252Fmonitors%252Fbelow-23-inches%252Frog-strix-xg17ahpe-model%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAHPE%3C%2Fa%3E%20version.%20Both%20are%20virtually%20identical%2C%20with%20the%20only%20difference%20(other%20than%20price)%20being%20that%20the%20former%20includes%20a%20foldable%20tripod%20stand%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20doesn't.%20Although%20we've%20seen%20a%20few%20reports%20complaining%20about%20how%20wobbly%20the%20monitor%20can%20be%20on%20its%20tripod%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20nice%20bonus.%20You%20also%20get%20a%20cover%20(that%20can%20act%20as%20an%20impromptu%20stand%20in%20portrait%20or%20landscape)%20and%20a%20handy%20carry%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20touchscreen%5C%22%3EBest%20touchscreen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20not%20already%20know%20Espresso%2C%20the%20Australian%20display%20maker%2C%20but%20its%2017%20Pro%20touchscreen%20portable%20monitor%20is%20a%20creative%20professional's%20dream%20that%20can%20rival%20many%20dedicated%20drawing%20tablets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20it%20features%20a%20gorgeous%2017-inch%204K%20screen.%20The%20durable%20aluminum%20chassis%20and%20scratch-resistant%20glass%20mean%20it%20can%20go%20nearly%20anywhere.%20And%20for%20when%20working%20at%20a%20desk%20or%20table%2C%20it%20includes%20a%20nice%2C%20sturdy%20stand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20may%20not%20have%20the%20fastest%20refresh%20rate%20or%20response%20time%2C%20both%20specs%20are%20adequate%20for%20tasks%20outside%20of%20high%20frame-rate%20gaming.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%2017%20Pro%20conveys%20gorgeous%20images%20and%20video%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%2010-bit%20color%20panel%20and%20support%20for%20the%20wide%20DCI-P3%20gamut.%20Moreover%2C%20its%20450%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness%20ensures%20those%20colors%20pop%20in%20various%20lighting%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20capacitive%20touchscreen%2C%20its%20raison%20d'etre%2C%20uses%20what%20Espresso%20calls%20its%20proprietary%20LiveTouch%20technology.%20The%20upshot%20is%20that%20the%2017%20Pro%20excels%20at%20taking%20inputs%20from%20writing%20and%20drawing%2C%20plus%20responding%20to%20various%20gesture%20controls.%20The%20optional%20pen%20accessory%20features%20a%20tail%20eraser%20and%20replaceable%20tip%20and%20is%20sensitive%20to%20tilting%20and%20over%204%2C000%20pressure%20levels.%20It's%20a%20shame%20the%20pen%20doesn't%20come%20included%2C%20but%20you%20can%20purchase%20it%20separately%20for%20%2489%20or%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%241%2C050%20bundle%20that%20also%20includes%20a%20stand%2C%20case%2C%20battery%2C%20and%20paper-like%20screen%20coating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20monitor%20features%20many%20wired%20connectivity%20options%2C%20including%20USB-C%2C%20HDMI%2C%20Mini%20DisplayPort%2C%20and%20DVI-D.%20And%20its%20built-in%20speakers%20automatically%20activate%20when%20the%2017%20Pro%20is%20connected%20to%20a%20secondary%20power%20source%20(i.e.%2C%20your%20laptop%20or%20a%20wall%20outlet).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20Espresso%20includes%20its%20Jot%20software%2C%20which%20works%20in%20tandem%20with%20popular%20productivity%20apps%20(Slides%2C%20PowerPoint%2C%20Keynote%2C%20Evernote%2C%20etc.)%20to%20help%20you%20take%20notes%2C%20draw%2C%20sketch%2C%20mark%20up%2C%20screenshot%2C%20and%20otherwise%20create%20and%20edit%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20wireless%5C%22%3EBest%20wireless%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20portable%20monitor%20that%20can%20work%20completely%20free%20from%20cables%2C%20then%20this%20Ricoh%20model%20is%20just%20what%20you're%20looking%20for.%20It%20supports%20USB-C%20and%20WiFi%205%20(802.11ac)%2C%20so%20it%20can%20connect%20wired%20or%20wirelessly%20to%20Windows%2C%20Mac%2C%20Android%2C%20and%20iOS%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20150BW%20supports%20wireless%20multicasting%20in%20either%20direction.%20This%20means%20the%20display%20can%20handle%20signals%20from%20up%20to%20two%20devices%20simultaneously%2C%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-cast-windows-desktop-to-tv%5C%22%3EMiracast%3C%2Fa%3E%20functionality.%20And%20it%20supports%20wirelessly%20multicasting%20to%20up%20to%20five%20other%20150BW%20monitors%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20making%20it%20a%20handy%20option%20for%20group%20presentations%20if%20your%20coworkers%20use%20the%20same%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ricoh150BW%20is%20also%20the%20only%20OLED%20monitor%20in%20this%20guide.%20OLED%20panels%20provide%20big%20contrast%20and%20viewing%20angle%20benefits%20over%20LCD%20technology%2C%20and%20OLED%20screens%20are%20used%20on%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20scratch-%20and%20shatter-proof%20glass%20display%20features%20multipoint%20capacitive%20touch%20as%20well.%20It's%20pretty%20svelte%20%E2%80%94%20claiming%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20lightest%2015.6-inch%20touchscreen%20portable%20monitors%20on%20the%20market%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20impressive%2C%20considering%20it%20also%20has%20an%20integrated%20battery%20to%20go%20wireless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20listed%20three%20hours%20of%20battery%20life%20isn't%20as%20long%20as%20we'd%20like%20for%20a%20wireless%20monitor.%20That's%20still%20enough%20to%20watch%20a%20movie%2C%20give%20in-person%20presentations%2C%20and%20tackle%20short%20productivity%20sessions%2C%20but%20isn't%20enough%20to%20get%20away%20with%20a%20full%20day%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20monitor's%20fantastic%20color%20gamut%2C%20built-in%201.5-watt%20speakers%2C%20and%20scorching%20max%20response%20time%20of%20one%20millisecond%20make%20it%20a%20solid%20choice%20for%20casual%20gaming.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20refresh%20rate%20is%20limited%20to%2060Hz%2C%20which%20is%20low%20compared%20to%20the%20144Hz-plus%20refresh%20rate%20that%20true%20gaming%20displays%20offer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERicoh%20also%20sells%20a%20compatible%20stylus%20pen%20capable%20of%204%2C096%20levels%20of%20pressure%20sensitivity.%20Given%20the%20price%2C%20we%20wish%20this%20was%20automatically%20bundled%20with%20the%20monitor%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20great%20option%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20portable%20monitors%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20portable%20monitors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20ViewSonic%20portable%20monitor%20paired%20with%20a%20wireless%20keyboard%20on%20a%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcf7ab6080194819fa4900%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20look%20for%20key%20specifications%20when%20recommending%20the%20best%20portable%20monitors.%3Cp%3EB%26amp%3BH%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20selected%20the%20best%20portable%20monitors%20based%20on%20hands-on%20experience%20and%20extensive%20research.%20In%20each%20case%2C%20we%20evaluated%20models%20with%20key%20performance%20areas%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20considered%20for%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20portable%20monitors%2C%20displays%20need%20to%20meet%20these%20minimum%20specifications%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFull%20HD%20(1920%20x%201080)%20resolution%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20least%20250%20to%20300%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20refresh%20rate%20of%2060Hz%20for%20productivity%20or%20at%20least%20144Hz%20for%20gaming%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20response%20time%20under%2010%20milliseconds%20for%20multimedia%20use%20or%20under%2030%20for%20productivity%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20that%20our%20picks%20remain%20as%20portable%20as%20possible%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20monitor%20sizes%20equivalent%20to%20most%20laptop%20screens%20(13%20to%2