The%20four-part%20saga%2C%20which%20premiered%20February%2015%2C%20tracks%20Barter's%20investigation%20into%20Mordecai%2C%20a%20former%20high%20school%20teacher%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20area%20city%20of%20Half%20Moon%20Bay.%20She%20speaks%20to%20Mordecai's%20family%20members%20and%20other%20alleged%20victims%2C%20building%20a%20disturbing%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20who%20many%20say%20bullied%20and%20terrorized%20them%20with%20violence%2C%20threats%2C%20and%20even%20rape%20until%20his%20death%20from%20cancer%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20series%2C%20Mordecai's%20family%20members%20and%20other%20women%20come%20forward%20to%20say%20they%20were%20viciously%20bullied%20and%20sexually%20or%20physically%20abused%20by%20the%20former%20Northern%20California%20teacher%2C%20who%20they%20also%20accuse%20of%20preying%20on%20teenage%20girls.%20One%20of%20his%20daughters%20recounts%20nightmares%20of%20being%20raped%20by%20him%2C%20and%20his%20former%20stepdaughter%2C%20Christi%20Probst%2C%20says%20she%20was%20sexually%20abused%20by%20him%20for%20years%2C%20starting%20when%20she%20was%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Barter%2C%20who%20was%20young%20when%20Mordecai%20died%2C%20the%20investigation%20was%20deeply%20personal%20on%20many%20levels.%20At%20the%20time%20she%20started%20digging%20into%20Mordecai%2C%20she%20says%20she%20was%20healing%20from%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20her%20life.%20She%20had%20gone%20back%20to%20school%20to%20study%20film%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20started%20writing%20about%20her%20family.%20A%20producer%20who%20came%20to%20her%20class%20asked%20whether%20Barter's%20story%20was%20true%20and%20put%20her%20in%20touch%20with%20Imagine%20Entertainment%2C%20a%20production%20company%20that%20in%20turn%20connected%20her%20with%20Borgman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorgman%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20deeply%20disturbing%20family%20sagas%2C%20and%20she%20gets%20plenty%20of%20pitches%20for%