er%20decided%20to%20follow%20that%20thread%2C%20unraveling%20it%20in%20real%20time%20during%20filming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20something%20that%20Sierra%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20family%20thought%20could%20be%20a%20possibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Borgman%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20set%20out%20early%20on%20to%20say%2C%20'Let's%20look%20at%20all%20the%20possibilities.%20Let's%20not%20just%20put%20something%20away%20because%20we%20don't%20think%20it%20could%20be%20this.%20Let's%20dive%20into%20it%2C%20let's%20do%20the%20investigation%2C%20let's%20ask%20the%20questions.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSierra%20never%20was%20like%2C%20'I'm%20certain%20it's%20this.'%20She%20was%20just%20like%2C%20'I%20want%20to%20find%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20Zodiac%20theory%20doesn't%20pan%20out%20%E2%80%94%20Barter%20meets%20with%20Zodiac%20expert%20Mike%20Butterfield%2C%20who%20concludes%20that%20there%20isn't%20compelling%20evidence%20to%20link%20Mordecai%20to%20the%20crimes.%20But%20in%20the%20final%20episode%20of%20the%20docuseries%2C%20Barter%20finally%20compiles%20all%20of%20her%20evidence%20linking%20Mordecai%20to%20the%20Santa%20Rosa%20killings%20and%20turns%20it%20over%20to%20the%20Sonoma%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20closing%20tag%20says%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20ongoing%2C%20and%20Borgman%20and%20Barter%20confirm%20that%20there%20are%20still%20no%20updates%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20Mordecai%20was%20the%20murderer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20though%2C%20proving%20whether%20Mordecai%20was%20a%20killer%20isn't%20the%20main%20point%20of%20the%20docuseries.%20It's%20about%20healing%20%E2%80%94%20Barter's%20own%20journey%20to%20healing%20after%20her%20sexual%20assaults%2C%20and%20how%20she%20facilitates%20her%20fractured%20family's%20healing%20after%20decades%20of%20trauma%20at%20Mordecai's%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20movingly%2C%20we%20see%20Barter's%20m