r%20of%20lions%20as%20Akbar%20and%20Sita%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagartala%2Ftripura-official-suspended-over-lioness-sita-row%2Farticleshow%2F107991610.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enews%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20the%20Kolkata%20high%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-name-animals-after-gods-historical-figures-asks-kolkata-hc-suggests-changing-lions-names%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20why%20the%20pair%20had%20been%20named%20after%20Akbar%20and%20Sita%20to%20cause%20potential%20religious%20controversies%2C%20after%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20filed%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epetition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20regarding%20this%20on%20February%2016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Akbar-Sita%20row%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lion%20and%20lioness%2C%20named%20%E2%80%98Akbar%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Sita%E2%80%99%20arrived%20at%20the%20North%20Bengal%20Wild%20Animals%20Park%20in%20Siliguri%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20from%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Sepahijala%20Zoo%20on%20February%2012%2C%20as%20part%20of%20an%20animal%20exchange%20programme%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagartala%2Ftripura-official-suspended-over-lioness-sita-row%2Farticleshow%2F107991610.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enews%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrabin%20Lal%20Agrawal%2C%20a%201994-batch%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%2C%20had%20recorded%20the%20name%20of%20the%20pair%20as%20Akbar%20and%20Sita%20in%20the%20dispatch%20register%20before%20sending%20them%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20Agrawal%20is%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%2C%20one%20of%20the%20topmost%20designations%20in%20the%20state%20forest%20department.%20He%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftripura.gov.in%2Findian-forest-service-cadre-tripura%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20(Wildlife%20and%20Tourism).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20the%20local%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20chapter%20filed%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epetition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20that%20later%20went%20as%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20High%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20regarding%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20pair%20as%20Akbar%20and%20Sita.%20VHP%20district%20chief%20Dulal%20Chandra%20Ray%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20naming%20came%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Hindu%20religion%3A%20Akbar%20is%20the%20name%20of%20a%20Mughal%20emperor%2C%20and%20Sita%20is%20a%20character%20in%20the%20Hindu%20epic%20Ramayan%2C%20also%20revered%20as%20a%20deity%20in%20the%20religion.%20The%20High%20Court%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20case%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversy%E2%80%9D%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%20It%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-name-animals-after-gods-historical-figures-asks-kolkata-hc-suggests-changing-lions-names%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20had%20named%20the%20animals%20in%20such%20a%20way%20and%20caused%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversy%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESenior%20forest%20official%20suspended%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EToI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20news%20report%2C%20the%20Tripura%20government%20sought%20a%20clarification%20from%20Agrawal%2C%20and%20he%20denied%20having%20named%20the%20pair%20Akbar%20and%20Sita.%20However%2C%20an%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwildlife%20officials%20in%20Tripura%E2%80%9D%20had%20given%20the%20names%2C%20per%20the%20news%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2024%2C%20the%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20currently%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%20the%20Indigenous%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20of%20Tripura%20%E2%80%93%20suspended%20Agrawal%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708965994000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17121846%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-10.43.15-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftripura-govt-suspends-chief-wildlife-warden-over-akbar-sita-row-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20comes%20after%20the%20Kolkata%20high%20court%20asked%20why%20the%20pair%20of%20lions%20had%20been%20named%20Akbar%20and%20Sita%2C%20to%20cause%20'controversy'%2C%20after%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20filed%20a%20petition%20regarding%20this%20on%20February%2016%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftripura-govt-suspends-chief-wildlife-warden-over-akbar-sita-row-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sweden%20set%20to%20become%20Nato%20member%20after%20Hungary%20ratifies%20bid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708965027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108020359%2Cimgsize-1144712.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fsweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid%2Farticleshow%2F108020284.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108020284.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHungary's%20parliament%20approved%20Sweden's%20NATO%20bid%2C%20the%20final%20step%20for%20its%20accession%20to%20the%20alliance%20amid%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20The%20ratification%2C%20with%20188%20votes%20in%20favor%20and%20six%20against%2C%20marks%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%20making%20Sweden%20the%2032nd%20NATO%20member.%20NATO%20Secretary-General%20Stoltenberg%20hailed%20the%20decision%2C%20emphasizing%20its%20significance%20for%20strengthening%20Euro-Atlantic%20security.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fsweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid%2Farticleshow%2F108020284.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fsweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid%2Famp_articleshow%2F108020284.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fsweden-set-to-become-nato-member-after-hungary-ratifies-bid%2Famp_articleshow%2F108020284.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hungary%20approves%20Sweden's%20bid%20to%20join%20NATO%20after%20months%20of%20delays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708964580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-sweden-hungary-nato_6470129.jpg%3F20240226195425%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhungary-approves-swedens-bid-to-join-nato-after-months-of-delays-13081690%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hungary's%20parliament%20has%20voted%20to%20ratify%20Sweden's%20bid%20to%20join%20NATO%2C%20clearing%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Nordic%20country%20to%20finally%20join%20the%20organisation%20almost%20two%20years%20after%20applying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhungary-approves-swedens-bid-to-join-nato-after-months-of-delays-13081690%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhungary-approves-swedens-bid-to-join-nato-after-months-of-delays-13081690%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhungary-approves-swedens-bid-to-join-nato-after-months-of-delays-13081690%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Compact%20Between%20Political%20and%20Economic%20Elite%20Distorts%20the%20Fight%20Against%20Corruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09155320%2FIMG_0444.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20and%20Congress%20stalwart%20Ashok%20Chavan%20switching%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20familiar%20spurt%20of%20arguments%20in%20the%20media%20eco-system%20which%20holds%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20squarely%20responsible%20for%20this%20defection.%20These%20arguments%20do%20not%20explain%20much%20but%20merely%20amplify%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20regime%20that%20there%20is%20no%20alternative%20to%20it%3B%20which%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20credible%20record%20of%20governance%2C%20is%20essential%20to%20its%20electoral%20strategy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20argument%20of%20deficient%20leadership%20does%20not%20hold%20for%20three%20reasons.%20First%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20defections%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20only%20one%20party%20but%20afflicts%20the%20entire%20opposition.%20Second%2C%20if%20the%20defections%20were%20merely%20the%20result%20of%20a%20fallout%20with%20the%20leadership%20or%20triggered%20by%20ideological%20disagreements%2C%20these%20politicians%20could%20have%20decided%20to%20form%20their%20own%20parties.%20There%20are%20numerous%20such%20examples%20in%20history%20from%20across%20the%20political%20divide.%20However%2C%20these%20defectors%20unfailingly%20join%20either%20the%20ruling%20party%20or%20the%20ruling%20coalition.%20Third%2C%20and%20most%20significantly%2C%20these%20defectors%20were%20invariably%20accused%20of%20corruption%20and%20were%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20even%20Chavan%20was%20accused%20of%20corruption%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20is%20not%20alone.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tactic%20of%20weaponising%20institutions%20to%20blackmail%20and%20co-opt%20the%20opposition%20has%20become%20common%20knowledge.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20an%20overstatement%20to%20say%20that%20by%20co-opting%20opposition%20leaders%20he%20once%20accused%20of%20corruption%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20decisively%20buried%20the%20issue%20altogether.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20rather%20than%20looking%20at%20these%20defections%20as%20isolated%20events%2C%20it%20would%20be%20much%20more%20analytically%20rewarding%20to%20look%20at%20them%20as%20the%20logical%20culmination%20of%20the%20political%20process%20which%20was%20set%20in%20motion%20by%20the%20anti-corruption%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDeliberately%20misunderstanding%20corruption%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20outset%2C%20it%20must%20be%20stated%20that%20the%20movement%20against%20corruption%20was%20bereft%20of%20any%20idea%20of%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20social%20or%20economic.%20While%20the%20ideas%20of%20social%20justice%20were%20conspicuously%20absent%20from%20the%20movement%2C%20the%20issues%20of%20economic%20justice%20were%20merely%20a%20derivative%20concern.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20argued%20that%20once%20the%20corrupt%20political%20elite%20was%20defeated%2C%20a%20more%20responsive%20and%20transparent%20state%20would%20address%20the%20redistributive%20concerns.%20However%2C%20the%20movement%20resolutely%20avoided%20offering%20a%20systemic%20understanding%20of%20corruption%2C%20thereby%20restricting%20its%20attack%20to%20the%20political%20elite%2C%20while%20maintaining%20a%20studied%20silence%20on%20the%20economic%20elite%20constituted%20by%20the%20rent-seeking%20corporate%20class%20which%20was%20equally%20complicit%20in%20and%20the%20prime%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20built%20his%20campaign%20upon%20this%20flawed%20understanding%20of%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption%20and%20converted%20the%202014%20election%20campaign%20into%20a%20referendum%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98corrupt%E2%80%99%20political%20elite.%20He%20promised%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20corruption%20through%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Lokpal%20and%20bring%20back%20black%20money%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20the%20honest%20tax%20payer.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20political%20elite%20was%20defeated%2C%20no%20such%20measures%20were%20initiated%20to%20tackle%20corruption%20except%20demonetisation%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20spectacular%20failure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20new%20elite%20compact%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20emerged%20rather%20was%20a%20new%20compact%20between%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20elite%20where%20the%20ruling%20regime%20ensured%20unfettered%20access%20to%20public%20resources%20to%20the%20corporate%20class%20in%20exchange%20for%20political%20funding%20and%20propaganda.%20Even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20observed%2C%20while%20declaring%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20unconstitutional%2C%20that%20the%20probability%20of%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%20could%20not%20be%20ruled%20under%20the%20opaque%20scheme.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecent%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20regime%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20the%20carrot%20and%20the%20stick%20to%20%E2%80%98extract%E2%80%99%20money%20from%20private%20donors.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20wholesale%20exodus%20of%20the%20corporate%20capital%20to%20the%20BJP%20which%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20recent%20disclosures%20on%20electoral%20bonds.%20According%20to%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20got%20six%20times%20more%20corporate%20funding%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20principal%20opposition%20and%20more%20than%20one%20and%20half%20times%20the%20funds%20of%20the%20remaining%20parties%20combined.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20return%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-write-off-rs-10-57-lakh-crore-in-five-years-make-npa-recovery-worth-rs-7-17-lakh-crore%2Farticleshow%2F105757525.cms%5C%22%3Ethe%20government%20wrote%20off%20loans%2C%20worth%20approximately%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20crores%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20pro-corporate%20bias%20of%20the%20regime%20is%20evident%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20government%20is%20now%20generating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fk-shape-widens-govt-personal-income-tax-collection-corporate-tax%5C%22%3Emore%20revenue%20from%20personal%20income%20tax%20rather%20than%20corporate%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20three%20decades.%20It%20has%20exacerbated%20the%20already%20existing%20levels%20of%20inequality%3B%20and%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20richest%20Indians%20has%20grown%20under%20its%20tenure%20while%20the%20masses%20struggle%20with%20inflation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fk-shape-widens-govt-personal-income-tax-collection-corporate-tax%5C%22%3EK-Shape%20Widens%3A%20In%205%20Years%2C%20Govt%20Tax%20Collection%20From%20Individuals%20up%20by%2076%25%2C%20From%20Corporates%20Only%20by%2024%25%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20great%20re-accommodation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20new%20compact%20severely%20distorted%20the%20level%20playing%20field%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20a%20functioning%20democracy.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20institutions%20gave%20rise%20to%20a%20much%20more%20authoritarian%20system%20%E2%80%93%20a%20change%20observed%20in%20the%20constant%20downgrading%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20credentials%20internationally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20the%20opposition%20was%20sufficiently%20weakened%2C%20prime%20minister%20Modi%20reneged%20on%20the%20last%20remaining%20promise%20of%20punishing%20the%20corrupt%20political%20elite%20and%20began%20co-opting%20them%20if%20they%20accepted%20his%20political%20and%20ideological%20patronage.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20began%20the%20process%20of%20re-accommodation%20of%20the%20defeated%20political%20elites%2C%20once%20branded%20corrupt%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20The%20process%20unleashed%20by%20the%20anti-corruption%20movement%2C%20which%20began%20with%20righteous%20disdain%20against%20the%20political%20elite%2C%20ended%20with%20their%20seamless%20co-option%20from%20the%20old%20to%20the%20new%20ruling%20dispensation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmergence%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpost-corruption%E2%80%9D%20polity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20today%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption%20does%20not%20find%20much%20space%20in%20the%20public%20discourse.%20This%20is%20primarily%20because%20the%20current%20opposition%20under%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20reversed%20the%20causation%20of%20corruption%20and%20targeted%20the%20rent-seeking%20economic%20elites.%20The%20Modi-regime%20neither%20punished%20the%20corrupt%20political%20elite%20nor%20reformed%20the%20system%3B%20rather%20used%20it%20instrumentally%20to%20attack%20the%20opposition%20while%20institutionalising%20corruption%20via%20electoral%20bonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20we%20have%20now%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpost-corruption%E2%80%9D%20polity.%20Where%20issues%20of%20transparency%2C%20rights%2C%20free%20media%20and%20justice%20have%20been%20replaced%20by%20national%20pride%2C%20corporate-led%20development%20and%20majoritarianism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20the%20movement%20against%20corruption%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20nothing%20but%20a%20trojan%20horse%20for%20the%20elite%20takeover%20of%20the%20economy%20under%20an%20increasingly%20autocratic%20political%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnshul%20Trivedi%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20political%20science%20from%20JNU%20and%20is%20currently%20a%20Congress%20worker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708964057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09155320%2FIMG_0444.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-compact-between-political-and-economic-elite-distorts-the-fight-against-corruption%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20movement%20against%20corruption%20was%20bereft%20of%20any%20idea%20of%20justice.%20It%20maintained%20a%20studied%20silence%20on%20the%20rent-seeking%20corporate%20class%20which%20was%20complicit%20and%20the%20prime%20beneficiary.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20built%20his%20campaign%20upon%20this%20flawed%20understanding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-compact-between-political-and-economic-elite-distorts-the-fight-against-corruption%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20wo