ing%20cleaning%20liquids%20for%20washing%20our%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20everything%20else%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20hygiene%20took%20centre-stage%2C%20was%20it%20unknowingly%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20careful%20assessment%20of%20multiple%20research%20papers%20made%20Simran%20get%20up%20and%20take%20action.%20She%20looked%20for%20safer%20alternatives%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20many%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20same%20prices%20as%20the%20regular%20cleaning%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20ingredients.%20Discovering%20many%20chemical%20names%20in%20everyday%20products%20was%20triggering%20for%20me%2C%20as%20they%20posed%20harm%20to%20my%20daughter.%20While%20doing%20home%20cleaning%2C%20I%20had%20a%20first-hand%20experience%20of%20how%20it%20was%20affecting%20my%20hands.%20I%20could%20see%20exactly%20what%20was%20being%20put%20in%20the%20bucket%2C%E2%80%9D%20Simran%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20that%20she%20realised%20that%20most%20conventional%20cleaners%20were%20laden%20with%20toxins.%20Unable%20to%20find%20any%20alternatives%2C%20she%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20develop%20products%20that%20would%20provide%20reassurance%20to%20mothers%20like%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275815%2Feco-friendly-cleaners-biodegradable-capsules-disinfectants-prevent-plastic-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformulating%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20omitted%20seven%20chemicals%20known%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20health%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20ammonia%2C%20chlorine%2C%20phosphates%2C%20EDTA%20(Ethylenediaminetetraacetic%20acid)%2C%20bleach%2C%20triclosan%2C%20and%20artificial%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20