3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20Article%20370%20move%2C%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20often%20closed%20by%20authorities%20on%20such%20occasions%20and%20a%20posse%20of%20gun-toting%20security%20personnel%20are%20deployed%20in%20strength%20at%20its%20main%20gates%20to%20turn%20away%20any%20worshippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20authorities%20have%20justified%20the%20crackdown%20citing%20fears%20of%20%E2%80%9Claw%20and%20order%20problems%E2%80%9D%20in%20and%20around%20the%20mosque%20which%20used%20to%20be%20an%20epicentre%20of%20anti-India%20and%20pro-freedom%20sentiment%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20managing%20body%20has%20termed%20the%20%E2%80%9Crepeated%20action%E2%80%9D%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattack%E2%80%9D%20on%20dissent%20and%20religious%20rights%20of%20Kashmiri%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20High%20Court%20granted%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20administration%20%E2%80%9Clast%20and%20final%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20which%20challenges%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20confinement%E2%80%9D%20of%20Mirwaiz%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chief%20cleric%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20in%20September%20last%20year%20to%20challenge%20his%20%E2%80%9Carbitrary%20and%20illegal%E2%80%9D%20detention%20after%20August%205%2C%202019%20when%20the%20BJP-led%20union%20government%20launched%20a%20sweeping%20crackdown%20in%20Kashmir%20with%20even%20three%20former%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20put%20under%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20managing%20body%2C%20Mirwaiz%20was%20allowed%20to%20offer%20prayers%20at%20the%20Jamia%20Masjid%20on%20three%20Fridays%20in%20more%20than%20four%20years%20after%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20bifurcated%20and%20downgraded%20into%20a%20union%20territory%2C%20including%20on%20September%2022%20last%20year%20when%20the%20administration%20lifted%20curbs%20on%20his%20Nigeen%20residence%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Jamia%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20curbs%20were%20imposed%20on%20both%20Mirwaiz%20and%20Jamia%20Masjid%20soon%20afterwards.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20then%20he%20has%20been%20prevented%20from%20going%20to%20Jamia%20Masjid%20on%20Fridays%20or%20addressing%20the%20faithful%20in%20any%20other%20mosque%20or%20religious%20congregations%20as%20the%20Mirwaiz%20(head%20priest).%20Whenever%20we%20approached%20the%20authorities%2C%20they%20have%20dilly%20dallied%20on%20the%20response%2C%20saying%20they%20will%20check%20with%20their%20higher%20ups%20and%20get%20back%2C%20which%20they%20never%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20aide%20of%20Mirwaiz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708954236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26174737%2FIMG_5806.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsrinagars-jamia-masjid-forcibly-closed-ahead-of-shab-e-baraat-prayers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%2C%20who%20was%20scheduled%20to%20deliver%20the%20sermon%2C%20was%20also%20placed%20under%20house%20arrest.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsrinagars-jamia-masjid-forcibly-closed-ahead-of-shab-e-baraat-prayers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macron%20to%20discuss%20Gaza%20with%20Qatar's%20Emir%20Al-Thani%20this%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708954021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108017380%2Cimgsize-723973.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmacron-to-discuss-gaza-with-qatars-emir-al-thani-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F108017353.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F1080173