%3ESubsequently%2C%20Tejashwi%20fanned%20out%20in%20the%20state%20on%20the%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Yatra%2C%20pulling%20a%20responsive%20crowd%20and%20focusing%20on%20employment%2C%20livelihood%2C%20rights%20of%20the%20weaker%20sections%20and%20youth%2C%20poverty%2C%20agriculture%2C%20health%2C%20deprivation%20and%20other%20issues%20concerning%20the%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20positivity%20%E2%80%98spills%20over%E2%80%99%20to%20SP%2C%20AAP%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpositivity%E2%80%9D%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20dice%20loaded%20against%20him%20probably%20inspired%20the%20scion%20of%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20in%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPutting%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%98blow%E2%80%99%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20dealt%20to%20him%20by%20poaching%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%2C%20Akhilesh%20moved%20on%20to%20sealing%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Congress.%20The%20SP%20got%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Khajuraho%20seat%20in%20its%20share%20and%20spared%2017%20seats%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20most%20populous%20state%2C%20injecting%20much%20needed%20confidence%20among%20the%20anti-BJP%20voters%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20refusing%20to%20be%20cowed%20down%20by%20the%20investigating%20agencies%E2%80%99%20relentless%20tirade%20on%20him%20and%20his%20party%20leaders%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20operated%20swiftly%20by%20sealing%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20importantly%20in%20Delhi%2C%20on%20which%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20expressed%20his%20doubts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPerception%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20now%20includes%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20governor%20Satyapal%20Malik%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaking%20his%20debut%20in%20parliamentary%20politics%20by%20getting%20elected%20as%20a%20Congress%20MLA%20from%20his%2