3E%3Cp%3EThe%20individual%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20not%20a%20frequent%20commenter%20on%20extreme%20right-wing%20sites%20and%20that%20YouTube%20was%2C%20for%20him%2C%20a%20far%20more%20significant%20source%20of%20information%20and%20inspiration.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAlthough%20he%20did%20frequent%20extreme%20right-wing%20discussion%20boards%20such%20as%20those%20on%204chan%20and%208chan%2C%20the%20evidence%20we%20have%20seen%20is%20indicative%20of%20more%20substantial%20use%20of%20YouTube%20and%20is%20therefore%20consistent%20with%20what%20he%20told%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20importance%20of%20online%20environments%20in%20radicalising%20lone%20actor%20terrorists%2C%20we%20questioned%20this%20and%20set%20out%20to%20investigate%20whether%20right-wing%20websites%20were%20important%20in%20Tarrant%E2%80%99s%20radicalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20found%20overturns%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20what%20we%20thought%20we%20knew%20about%20him.%20It%20also%20raises%20serious%20questions%20not%20only%20about%20why%20this%20posting%20was%20not%20detected%20before%20the%20attack%20but%20also%20why%20it%20has%20not%20been%20discovered%20in%20the%20five%20years%20since%20the%20March%2015%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeyond%20the%20manifesto%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20Tarrant%20interact%20candidly%20with%20his%20online%20community%2C%20we%20see%20that%20much%20of%20what%20he%20stated%20in%20his%20manifesto%20was%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20manifesto%20that%20he%20was%20driven%20to%20violence%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20political%20solution%20%E2%80%93%20a%20realisation%20that%20came%20to%20him%20in%202017%20%E2%80%93%20we%20now%20know%20he%20had%20been%20calling%20for%20attacks%20against%20civilians%20at%20least%20as%20early%20as%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20he%20claimed%20he%20was%20not%20driven%20by%20antisemitism%2C%20we%20found%20hatred%20and%20conspiratorial%20distrust%20of%20Jews%20were%20central%20to%20his%20entire%20worldview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20claimed%20in%20his%20manifesto%20that%20he%20carried%20out%20his%20attack%20to%20preserve%20diversity%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20cultures%2C%20the%20violent%20racism%20and%20Islamophobia%20in%20his%20posting%20sets%20him%20apart%2C%20even%20in%20the%20darkest%20corners%20of%204chan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20be%20publishing%20more%20about%20Tarrant%E2%80%99s%20online%20history%2C%20including%20what%20radicalised%20him%20and%20what%20lessons%20can%20be%20learned.%20Here%20we%20introduce%20some%20of%20our%20initial%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20revelations%2C%20we%20show%20that%20there%20were%20numerous%20opportunities%20for%20the%20public%20and%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australian%20security%20services%20to%20observe%20him%20making%20very%20threatening%20statements%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20chosen%20to%20repeat%20only%20a%20small%20number%20of%20Tarrant%E2%80%99s%20statements%2C%20given%20their%20highly%20offensive%20nature.%20However%2C%20we%20still%20advise%20caution%20before%20reading%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20found%20the%20posts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%204chan%20posts%20are%20anonymous%2C%20we%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20indicators%20to%20identify%20Tarrant.%204chan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20incorrect%E2%80%9D%20board%20%E2%80%93%20referred%20to%20as%20%2Fpol%2F%20%E2%80%93%20provides%20the%20time%2C%20date%20and%20location%20of%20each%20post%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20match%20this%20against%20Tarrant%E2%80%99s%20travel%20to%20numerous%20countries%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarrant%20also%20frequently%20provided%20personal%20information%20in%20his%20posts%2C%20and%20he%20used%20the%20same%20distinctive%20language.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20he%20repeated%20points%20we%20know%20he%20made%20elsewhere.%20He%20openly%20and%20proudly%20stated%20his%20Australian%20identity%2C%20even%20as%20he%20called%20for%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20often%20made%20specific%20grammatical%20errors%20which%20make%20his%20posting%20stand%20out.%20He%20uses%20this%20style%20in%20online%20writing%20samples%20as%20early%20as%202011%2C%20in%20his%202019%20manifesto%2C%20and%20in%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20online%20posting%20in%20between.%20In%20combination%2C%20these%20indicators%20identify%20Tarrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26174821%2FPatsy_Reddy_lays_flowers_at_Hagley_Park.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26174821%2FPatsy_Reddy_lays_flowers_at_Hagley_Park.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26174821%2FPatsy_Reddy_lays_flowers_at_Hagley_Park-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26174821%2FPatsy_Reddy_lays_flowers_at_Hagley_Park-1024x684.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698978%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20lay%20flowers%20at%20Christchurch%20Botanic%20Gardens%20for%20those%20killed%20in%20mosque%20attacks.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FGovernment%20House%2C%20New%20Zealand%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20team%20of%20four%20researchers%20reviewed%20thousands%20of%20anonymous%20posts%20and%20hundreds%20of%20threads%20on%20%2Fpol%2F.%20We%20used%20the%20platform%E2%80%99s%20search%20function%20for%20particular%20words%2C%20phrases%20and%20images.%20As%20a%20team%20we%20carefully%20evaluated%20all%20posts%20which%20included%20several%20of%20the%20above%20indicators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20maintained%20a%20very%20high%20evidence%20threshold%20for%20including%20posts%20in%20our%20analysis.%20We%20excluded%20some%20important%20statements%20that%20were%20almost%20certainly%20written%20by%20him%2C%20but%20for%20which%20only%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20above%20indicators%20were%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20found%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202015%2C%20Tarrant%20was%20calling%20for%20mass%20violence%20against%20people%20of%20colour.%20Inspired%20by%20Dylann%20Roof%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2020%2F06%2F17%2F878828088%2F5-years-after-charleston-church-massacre-what-have-we-learned%5C%22%3Emassacre%20of%20nine%20Black%20worshippers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20church%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20Tarrant%20excitedly%20claimed%20%E2%80%9Cviolence%20is%20the%20last%20resort%20of%20a%20cornered%20animal%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20always%20going%20to%20come%20to%20this%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20here%20Tarrant%20made%20clear%20that%20white%20nationalist%20extremists%20should%20target%20innocent%20victims%20in%20locations%20of%20%E2%80%9Csignificance%E2%80%9D%2C%20such%20as%20places%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20other%20posters%20claimed%20Roof%20should%20have%20targeted%20a%20%E2%80%9Cghetto%E2%80%9D%2C%20Tarrant%20became%20frustrated.%20He%20explained%20that%20attacking%20unarmed%20people%20in%20a%20church%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20simple%20tactic%E2%80%9D%20necessary%20to%20provoke%20people%20of%20colour%20into%20retaliating.%20He%20used%20a%20highly%20racist%20phrase%20common%20on%20the%20%2Fpol%2F%20board%20to%20refer%20to%20this%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20at%20least%20four%20years%2C%20then%2C%20Tarrant%20contemplated%20and%20planned%20on%20killing%20people%20in%20a%20location%20of%20emotional%20importance%20such%20as%20a%20school%20or%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20glorified%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20violence%2C%20including%20school%20and%20public%20shootings%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20which%20were%20driven%20by%20psychological%20or%20other%20motives%20rather%20than%20white%20nationalist%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20advocated%20for%20and%20praised%20the%20sadistic%20and%20brutal%20killing%20of%20innocent%20civilians.%20The%20key%20for%20Tarrant%20was%20that%20this%20violence%20was%20perpetrated%20by%20white%20men.%20For%20him%2C%20any%20white%20violence%20might%20trigger%20the%20race%20war%20and%20segregation%20he%20desired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20travelled%20the%20world%20between%202014%20and%202018%2C%20Tarrant%20became%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20Muslims.%20His%20hatred%20persisted%20after%20arriving%20in%20New%20Zealand.%20Sometimes%20it%20spiralled%20into%20unhinged%20tirades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20thread%2C%20he%20claimed%20he%20would%20form%20and%20fund%20an%20armed%20band%20of%204chan%20users%20to%20conduct%20ethnic%20cleansing%20in%20the%20Balkans.%20Some%20of%20his%20posting%20is%20unusually%20violent%20even%20within%20the%20extremism%20of%20%2Fpol%2F.%20With%20hindsight%20at%20least%2C%20it%20suggests%20potential%20opportunities%20for%20detection%2C%20most%20obviously%20by%20Australian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20that%20same%20thread%2C%20he%20identified%20himself%20as%20Australian%20four%20times%2C%20and%20brazenly%20wrote%20there%20was%20nothing%20the%20Australian%20government%20could%20do%20to%20stop%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%20of%20this%20violent%20fantasy%2C%20he%20emailed%20a%20gun%20club%20in%20Dunedin%20stating%20his%20plans%20to%20move%20to%20New%20Zealand.%20In%20the%20same%20week%2C%20he%20made%20donations%20to%20international%20far-right%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperational%20Security%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20royal%20commission%20into%20the%20Christchurch%20terror%20attacks%20concluded%20Tarrant%20made%20only%20%E2%80%9Climited%20lapses%E2%80%9D%20in%20operational%20security%20during%20his%20time%20in%20New%20Zealand%20between%20late%202017%20and%20March%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20case.%20He%20posted%20regularly%20on%20%2Fpol%2F%2C%20which%20is%20freely%20and%20publicly%20accessible.%20His%20posting%20was%20visible%20to%20numerous%20others%20whose%20identities%20he%20could%20not%20possibly%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20threads%20in%20March%20and%20August%20of%202018%20in%20particular%20show%20his%20hatred%20of%20and%20plans%20to%20attack%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20As%20such%2C%20they%20presented%20opportunities%20for%20his%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20threads%2C%20Tarrant%20and%20other%20users%20posted%20angrily%20about%20the%20spread%20of%20immigrants%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20particularly%20the%20presence%20of%20mosques%20in%20small%20towns.%20Very%20soon%2C%20a%20group%20of%20anonymous%20posters%2C%20including%20Tarrant%2C%20discussed%20violence%20against%20the%20buildings%20(and%20the%20communities%20that%20gather%20in%20them).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20another%20user%20posted%20an%20image%20of%20a%20box%20of%20matches%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20mosques%2C%20Tarrant%20wrote%20%E2%80%9CSoon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevealing%20he%20was%20in%20Dunedin%2C%20Tarrant%20expressed%20his%20anger%20at%20the%20presence%20of%20mosques%20in%20that%20city%2C%20and%20in%20Christchurch%20and%20Ashburton%20to%20the%20north%2C%20using%20highly%20abusive%20language.%20When%20other%20users%20called%20on%20him%20to%20act%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20stop%20it.%20Just%20hold%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%20from%20maintaining%20tight%20operational%20security%20as%20he%20planned%20his%20attack%2C%20Tarrant%20openly%20(albeit%20anonymously)%20discussed%20violence%20against%20mosques%20in%20the%20South%20Island%20while%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventing%20it%20happening%20again%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%204chan%20community%20was%20crucial%20in%20Tarrant%E2%80%99s%20radicalisation%20(and%20the%20examples%20given%20here%20are%20just%20a%20portion%20of%20what%20we%20have%20found).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F19434472.2020.1862274%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20online%20environments%20in%20the%20radicalisation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20other%20white%20nationalist%20terrorists%2C%20it%20is%20disturbing%20this%20aspect%20of%20Tarrant%E2%80%99s%20path%20to%20March%2015%20has%20not%20been%20investigated%20more%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20his%20final%20words%20before%20the%20attack%20were%20released%20on%20the%20imageboard%208chan%2C%20but%20also%20intended%20for%204chan%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20long%20ride%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20you%20are%20all%20top%20blokes%20and%20the%20best%20bunch%20of%20cobbers%20a%20man%20could%20ask%20for%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20hard%20to%20imagine%20a%20clearer%20signpost%20that%20the%20real%20nature%20of%20his%20radicalisation%20could%20be%20found%20on%20those%20forums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20later%2C%20it%20seems%20we%20are%20only%20beginning%20to%20understand%20why%20he%20committed%20the%20atrocity%2C%20what%20might%20have%20been%20done%20to%20stop%20it%2C%20and%20how%20government%20agencies%20can%20work%20together%20with%20specialist%20extremism%20researchers%20to%20prevent%20it%20happening%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMore%20information%20about%20our%20study%20will%20be%20released%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heiaglobal.com%2F%5C%22%3Eheiaglobal.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20research%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Auckland%20Human%20Participant%20Ethics%20Committee.%20A%20paper%20based%20on%20this%20study%20has%20been%20submitted%20for%20peer%20review%20and%20publication.%3C