ta%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20Brigade%20Parade%20grounds%20on%20March%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20MP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Bikash%20Ranjan%20Bhattacharya%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTMC%E2%80%99s%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20is%20entirely%20in%20the%20shelter%20of%20the%20state%20police.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20stay%20of%20three%20months%20on%20the%20state%20CID%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20ABP%20Ananda%20vice-president%20and%20journalist%20Suman%20De.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20anchor%20has%20repeatedly%20apologised%20for%20the%20false%20news%20that%20was%20aired.%20While%20it%20may%20be%20probed%20as%20to%20why%20this%20news%20was%20aired%2C%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20are%20not%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Justice%20Kaushik%20Chanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETMC%20leader%20held%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sandeshkhali%20itself%2C%20there%20has%20been%20heavy%20police%20and%20security%20force%20presence%20at%20the%20houses%20of%20TMC%20leaders%2C%20which%20are%20often%20being%20stormed%20by%20angry%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20February%2026%2C%20villagers%20attacked%20the%20house%20of%20a%20TMC%20leader%20from%20Bermajur%2C%20Shankar%20Sardar.%20Sarkar%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gram%20Panchayat.%20Local%20women%20alleged%20that%20Shankar%20used%20guns%20to%20intimidate%20them%20often%20and%20is%20close%20to%20TMC%20ministers.%20Locals%20alleged%20that%20along%20with%20another%20strongman%2C%20Tapan%20Sardar%2C%20Shankar%20used%20to%20also%20take%20away%20the%20daily%20wages%20earned%20by%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20weekend%2C%20angry%20villagers%20had%20also%20stormed%20the%20house%20of%20local%20heavyweight%20Ajit%20Maity.%20Maity%20fled%20and%20took%20shelter%20at%20a%20civic%20volunteer%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Police%20eventually%20took%20him%20into%20custody.%20Climbing%20onto%20a%20police%20jeep%2C%20Maity%20told%20reporters%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20a%20BJP%20worker%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20joined%20TMC%20in%202019.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20these%20earlier%20complaints%20against%20me%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20are%20resolute%20that%20Maity%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20strong-arming%20tactics%20had%20been%20in%20place%20even%20before.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20always%20tortured%20the%20poor.%20He%20took%20our%20land%20earlier%20as%20well.%20Greed%20drove%20him%20to%20the%20TMC%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20one%20Nirmala%20Sardar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETMC%20ministers%20visit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20leaders%20of%20a%20beleaguered%20TMC%20held%20public%20meetings%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20Villagers%2C%20armed%20with%20brooms%20and%20sticks%2C%20stopped%20Sujit%20Bose%20and%20Partha%20Bhowmick%20on%20the%20tracks.%20The%20two%20had%20to%20hold%20their%20meeting%20at%20the%20Bermajur%20School.%20With%20Ajit%20Maity%20behind%20bars%2C%20Bose%20and%20Bhowmik%20announced%20that%20Haladhar%20Ari%20and%20Shaktipada%20Raut%20would%20take%20over%20temporary%20charge%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20local%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20irrigation%20minister%20Bhowmick%20claimed%20the%20allegations%20of%20wrongdoing%20were%20not%20exactly%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20some%20people%20have%20been%20mentally%20tortured%20but%20never%20physically.%20We%20will%20not%20spare%20anyone%20who%20has%20stolen%20land%20in%20the%20Bengal%20ruled%20by%20Didi%20%5BCM%20Mamata%20Banerjee%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhowmick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20ministers%20then%20participated%20in%20a%20kirtan%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20harvested%20grains%20stored%20at%20the%20newly%20appointed%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20chief%20Haladhar%20Ari%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20set%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%