%20that%20the%20Greenway%20Smart%20Stove%20comes%20with%20a%20patented%20air%20regulation%20technology%20that%20leads%20to%20better%20combustion%2C%20thereby%20increasing%20efficiency%20and%20reducing%20smoke.%20They%20have%20two%20models%3A%20the%20Smart%20Stove%20at%20Rs%202%2C199%2C%20and%20the%20Jumbo%20Stove%20at%20Rs%203%2C499%20for%20bigger%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stove%20has%20a%20single%20burner%20and%20works%20on%20different%20solid%20biomass%20fuels%2C%20such%20as%20wood%2C%20dry%20dung%2C%20crop%20waste%2C%20coconut%20waste%2C%20and%20bamboo.%20It%20reduces%20cooking%20time%20and%20is%20portable.%20The%20most%20important%20benefit%20of%20this%20stove%2C%20Ankit%20claims%2C%20is%20that%20it%20helps%20save%2065%20percent%20of%20fuel%20and%20reduces%20smoke%20by%2070%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20product%20eliminates%20carbon%20monoxide%20from%20burning%20firewood.%20It%20reduces%20smoke%20emissions%2C%20making%20it%20safer%20for%20kitchen%20or%20household%20use.%20Unlike%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Echulhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20often%20cause%20burns%2C%20this%20stove%20poses%20less%20risk%20of%20burns%20for%20women%20and%20children.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20reduces%20eye%20irritation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20environmental%20impact%20is%20concerned%2C%20Ankit%20states%20that%20each%20smart%20stove%20reduces%20greenhouse%20emissions%20by%20at%20least%20two%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20For%20the%20women%20using%20these%20stoves%2C%20besides%20the%20health%20aspect%2C%20their%20cooking%20time%20is%20greatly%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalita%2C%20who%20used%20to%20wake%20up%20at%204%20am%2C%20now%20rises%20at%205%20am%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20improved%20stove.%20She%20notes%20that%20cooking%20has%20become%20faster%20with%20the%20Smart%20stove%2C%20which%20she%20has%20been%20using%20for%20the%20past%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20stove%20involves%20much%20less%20cleaning%20as%20ash%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fall%20on%20the%20floor.%20The%20firewood%20which%20we%20used%20to%20collect%20would%20last%20us%20for%20just%20two%20days%20earlier%2C%20now%20it%20lasts%20us%20for%2015%20to%2020%20days.%20Food%20is%20also%20made%20on%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20time%20spent%20collecting%20firewood%20has%20also%20reduced%20greatly%2C%20leaving%20her%20with%20more%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20customer%2C%20Geeta%20Rahangdale%2C%20says%20that%20it%20has%20made%20the%20kitchen%20cooler%20and%20uses%20very%20little%20firewood.%20She%20also%20appreciates%20the%20fact%20that%20food%20can%20be%20made%20anywhere%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20bargaining%20power%20to%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBjeJw_mFNAz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBjeJw_mFNAz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBjeJw_mFNAz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Greenway%20Appliances%20(%40greenwayappliances)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20product%20was%20well-received%2C%20Ankit%20discovered%20that%20many%20potential%20customers%20were%20not%20purchasing%20it.%20He%20realised%20that%20while%20women%20were%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20cooking%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20they%20often%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20funds%20or%20bargaining%20power%20to%20buy%20the%20stoves%20outright.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20Ankit%20and%20his%20team%20began%20collaborating%20with%20rural%20retail%20shops%2C%20micro-finance%20institutions%2C%20self-help%20groups%2C%20and%20local%20NGOs.%20They%20developed%20financial%20packages%20through%20these%20institutions%20to%20allow%20women%20to%20purchase%20the%20product%20through%20easy%20instalments.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20corporate%20companies%20to%20subsidise%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20outreach%20across%20villages%20happens%20through%20the%20Greenway%20team.%20We%20have%20implementation%20and%20financing%20partners%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20woman%20should%20be%20able%20to%20avail%20the%20benefits%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329333%2Fbiodegradable-eco-biotraps-prasad-phadke-reduce-mosquito-population-dengue-malaria-zika%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaner%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20are%20also%20working%20with%20sustainability%20partners%20to%20provide%20carbon%20offsets%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20they%20noticed%20higher%20sales%20in%20South%20India%2C%20where%20there%E2%80%99s%20greater%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%20have%20more%20access%20to%20cash.%20Over%20time%2C%20sales%20began%20to%20increase%20nationwide.%20To%20date%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20over%20three%20million%20stoves%20across%20India%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20and%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20a%20factory%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20over%20500%20employees.%20Ankit%E2%80%99s%20vision%20is%20to%20reach%2020%20million%20households%20by%202030.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20keep%20designing%20products%20that%20increase%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20rural%20households.%20I%20also%20aspire%20to%20reach%20more%20customers%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708435145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%2C%20co-founded%20by%20Ankit%20Mathur%20and%20Neha%20Juneja%2C%20innovated%20the%20'Smart%20Stove'%20as%20an%20efficient%20cooking%20solution%20and%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20'chulhas'.%20It%20cuts%20smoke%2C%20saves%20fuel%2C%20and%20helps%20rural%20women%20save%20time%20and%20effort%20while%20reducing%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342452%2Ftraditional-chulha-smoke-while-cooking-greenway-grameen-ankit-mathur-neha-juneja-smart-stove%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20If%20Each%20Indian%20Could%20Sponsor%20Nutrition%20For%201%20Malnourished%20Child%3F%20IAS%20Officer%20Makes%20it%20Possible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20September%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20Pooja%20Bai%20Kol%E2%80%99s%20toddler%20Deepanshu%20fell%20sick.%20For%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20her%20son%20suffered%20severe%20diarrhoea%2C%20making%20him%20so%20weak%20that%20the%20family%20had%20to%20admit%20him%20to%20the%20nearby%20