0and%20mother%20of%20two%20had%20long%20harboured%20a%20dream%20of%20%E2%80%98doing%20something%E2%80%99%20and%20making%20a%20name%20for%20herself.%20When%20she%20saw%20that%20two%20homemakers%20had%20been%20able%20to%20create%20a%20business%20out%20of%20a%20skill%20she%20had%20mastered%2C%20she%20knew%20that%20she%20had%20found%20her%20calling.%20Her%20pickles%2C%20especially%20her%20mango%20pickle%2C%20were%20always%20in%20demand%20with%20relatives%20and%20friends%20making%20a%20beeline%20for%20it%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20her%20son%2C%20Amit%20Prajapati%2C%20runs%20a%20brand%20building%20and%20digital%20marketing%20agency.%20The%2019-year-old%20quickly%20set%20up%20social%20media%20pages%20under%20their%20brand%20name%20Moms%20Magic%20Pickle%20India%20in%20June%202023%2C%20ran%20a%20few%20ads%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20they%20had%20their%20first%20order.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaroj%20would%20make%20and%20pack%20the%20pickle%20and%20Amit%20helped%20her%20brand%2C%20label%20and%20dispatch%20it.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20their%20business%20grew%20and%20they%20had%20to%20set%20up%20a%20bigger%20space%20and%20hire%20women.%20Today%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20sells%20over%20800%20pickles%20per%20month%20and%20earns%20Rs%202.5%20lakhs%20per%20month%20seven%20months%20after%20starting%20her%20business.%20The%20woman%20who%20never%20set%20foot%20in%20a%20school%20is%20providing%20employment%20to%2030%20women%20today%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20she%20set%20up%20a%20business%20from%20scratch%20with%20no%20prior%20experience%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20her%20incredible%20story%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20made%20my%20first%20pickle%20at%2015%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20853px)%20100vw%2C%20853px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com