n.%20But%20her%20husband%2C%20Bablu%20Prajapati%2C%20always%20encouraged%20her%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20had%20seen%20before%20marriage%20was%20our%20village.%20My%20husband%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339969%2Fadil-qadri-attar-perfumes-shark-tank-india-entrepreneur-asthma-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanted%20me%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20matters%20of%20local%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saroj%20shares%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20opportunity%20presented%20itself%20to%20contribute%20to%20her%20community%2C%20she%20grabbed%20it%2C%20and%C2%A0%20served%20as%20the%20village%20sarpanch%20for%20eight%20years.%20During%20her%20tenure%2C%20she%20met%20many%20women%20from%20rural%20areas%20and%20learnt%20about%20their%20financial%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20then%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20help%20provide%20an%20income%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20stepped%20down%2C%20she%20became%20busy%20discharging%20duties%20at%20home.%20Soon%2C%20both%20her%20children%20left%20for%20college%20and%20she%20was%20left%20with%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20build%20something.%20She%20got%20the%20answer%20for%20her%20%E2%80%98what%20to%20do%E2%80%99%20after%20watching%20the%20two%20women%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20it%20so%20happened%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20making%20pickles%20at%20the%20time%20as%20mangoes%20were%20in%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20relative%20or%20friend%20who%20comes%20home%20during%20the%20mango%20season%20always%20takes%20a%20pickle%20jar%20home.%20Everyone%20who%20tastes%20it%20becomes%20a%20fan.%20I%20thought%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20perfect%20business%20opportunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStarted%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaroj2-1708351324.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amit%20helped%20Saroj%20with%20the%20digital%20marketing%2C%20packaging%20of%20the%20business%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaroj2-1708351324.jpeg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaroj2-1708351324-220x300.jpeg%20220w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaroj2-1708351324-500x683.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaroj2-1708351324-150x205.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342287%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22983%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmit%20helped%20Saroj%20with%20the%20digital%20marketing%2C%20packaging%20of%20the%20business%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20the%20family%20did%20was%20order%20other%20homemade%20pickles%20to%20check%20the%20taste%2C%20packaging%20and%20pricing.%20After%20assessing%20their%20competitors%2C%20Amit%2C%20who%20stays%20in%20Indore%2C%20worked%20on%20the%20design%20and%20name%20of%20the%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20SEO%20on%20YouTube%20and%20decided%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300822%2Fsenior-citizen-entrepreneur-sheila-pickles-jams-traditional-kerala-recipes-home-business-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoms%20Magic%20Pickle%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20a%20good%20name.%20I%20set%20up%20Facebook